quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaf ngeQur’an enedumela elikhulu
  50,2,"Kepha bayamangala ukuthi kufike kubona umxwayisi ophuma phakathi kwabo, ngakho-ke abangakholwa bathi, “lokhu yinto emangalisayo”"
  50,3,Ngakube uma sesifile sabawuthuli – lokho ukuphindela okukude
  50,4,"Ngempela siyakwazi lokho umhlaba okunciphisayo kubona, ikanye nathi incwadi elondolozayo"
  50,5,"Kepha baliphika iqiniso ngenkathi lifika kubona, ngakho-ke bona basesimweni esididayo"
  50,6,Ngakube ababheki yini esibhakabhakeni ngaphezulu kwabo ukuthi sasakha kanjani futhi sasenza sabukeka sisihle futhi asinayo imifantu
  50,7,Nomhlaba sawendlala futhi sabeka kuwona izintaba futhi samilisa kuwona zonke izinhlobo zezithelo nemithi ngambili
  50,8,Ukubona nesikhumbuzo kuleyo naleyo nceku ephendukela kuMvelinqangi ngokuzisola
  50,9,Futhi sawehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni abusisekile sabe sesenza ngawo ukuthi kumile izivande nohlamvu lokuvunwayo
  50,10,Nezihlahla ezinde zesundu ezinezixheke ezilekene ezivuthiwe
  50,11,Isabelo sezinceku (zikaMvelinqangi) futhi saphilisa ngawo (amanzi) izwe elifile kunjalo ukuphuma (ukuvuka kwabafileyo)
  50,12,Baphika ngaphambilini kwabo abantu baNowa nezihlali zaseRass nezaseThamud
  50,13,No A’d noFaro kanye nabafowabo ka-Lothi
  50,14,"Nezihlali zase-Aykah kanye nabantu baseTubba, bonke babeziphika izithunywa ngakho-ke yabe seyiyagcwaliseka insongo yami"
  50,15,Ngakube sehluleka yini endaweni yokuqala? Kepha bona basekudidekeni ngendawo entsha
  50,16,Futhingempelasamudalaumuntufuthisakwazilokhoubuyena obuhleba ngakho kuyena futhi thina sisondele kakhulu kuyena kunomthambo (wakhe) omkhulu osentanyeni
  50,17,Ngenkathi abemukeli ababili (izingelosi) bemukela behleli omunye ngakwesokudla omunye ngakwesobunxele
  50,18,Akaliphimisi igama ngaphandle kokuthi eduzane naye kunomalusi (umqaphi) olindile
  50,19,"Futhi ukudalwa kokufa kuyofika ngeqiniso, lokho kuyilokho wena owawuzama ukukugwema"
  50,20,"Futhi icilongo liyofuthwa, lolo wusuku lwensongo"
  50,21,Futhi lowo nalowo mphefumulo uyoza kanye nomshayeli nofakazi
  50,22,"Ngempela wawungakunakile lokho, ngakho-ke sisisusile kuwena isembozo sakho futhi ukubona kwakho namhlanje kubukhali"
  50,23,"Futhi okanye naye (ingelosi) iyothi, “nakhu lokhu okukanye nami kulungile"
  50,24,(UMvelinqangi uyothi ezingelosini) nobabili phonsani esihogweni lowo nalowo ongakholwa onenkani
  50,25,"Umenqabeli wokuhle, umephuli womthetho umngabazi"
  50,26,Lowo obeka omunye unkulunkulu kanye noMvelinqangi ngakho-ke nobabili muphonseni esijezisweni esinzima
  50,27,"Okanye naye uyothi, “Nkosi yethu angizange ngimdukise kepha wayesekudukeni okukude”"
  50,28,"Uyothi, “musani ukuphikisana ngaphambili kwami kulapho sengasidlulisela kunina isexwayiso”"
  50,29,Ayiguqulwa inkulumo lapha kumina futhi mina angisiyena ongenabo ubulungiswa ezincekwini
  50,30,"Ngosuku khumbula lapho sithi esihogweni, “ngakube ugcwele yini na?” Siyothi (isihogo) “ngakube bakhona yini abanye)”"
  50,31,Futhi siyosondezwa isivande (kulabo) abagwema okubi hayi kude
  50,32,Lokhu kuyilokhu enethenjiswa kona – kulowo nalowo ophendukela (kuMvelinqangi) ogcina isethembiso
  50,33,Lowo omesabayo onomusa ngasese futhi ozoza nenhliziyo yokuzisola
  50,34,Ngenani kusona ngokuthula lolu wusuku lwangunaphakade
  50,35,Okwabo lapho phakathi yilokho abakufisayo futhi kuthina kunokungaphezulu
  50,36,Futhi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo zona zazinamandla amakhulu ngaphezulu kwabo futhi zazihamba emhlabeni ngakube ikhona yini indawo yokuphephela
  50,37,Ngempela kulokho kunesikhumbuzo kunoma ngabe ngubani onenhliziyo noma onika ukuzwa kulapho yena engufakazi
  50,38,Futhi ngempela sawadala amazulu nomhlaba nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ezinsukwini eziyisithupha futhi akuzange kusithinte ukukhathala
  50,39,Ngakho-ke kubekezelele lokho abakushoyo futhi ugubhe indumiso yeNkosi yakho ngaphambili kokukhuphuka kwelanga nangaphambili kokushona (kwelanga)
  50,40,Nasebusuku yidumise nangemumva kokuwa phansi niguqa
  50,41,Futhi lalela ngosuku lapho ummemezi ememeza endaweni eseduze
  50,42,Usuku lapho beyobe bezwa umsindo (ukukhaliswa kwecilongo) kweqiniso lolo kuyoba wusuku emathuneni
  50,43,Ngempela thina siyaphilisa futhi siyabulala futhi kukuthina ukubuyela kokugcina
  50,44,Usuku lapho umhlaba uyodabuka usuke kubona ngokushesha lokho kuqoqa kuthina kulula
  50,45,"Thina sikwazi kangcono lokho abakushoyo futhi wena awusiyena umphoqi kubona, ngakho-ke khumbuza ngeQur’an lowo owesaba ukusonga kwami"
  51,1,Ngifunga ngemimoya esakazayo
  51,2,Ngifunga nangamafu athwele
  51,3,Ngifunga nangemikhumbi ehamba kalula
  51,4,Ngifunga nangababa udaba
  51,5,Ngempela lokho enethenjiswa kona kuyiqiniso
  51,6,Futhi ngempela ukwahlulelwa kuzokwenzeka
  51,7,Ngifunga ngezulu eligcwele ubuhle
  51,8,Ngempela nina nisenkulumweni ephikisanayo
  51,9,Osusiwe kuyona yilowo ophambukisiwe
  51,10,Ababhujiswe abaqamba amanga
  51,11,Labo abangaphansi kwesembozo sokunganaki
  51,12,Babuza ukuthi lunini usuku lokwahlulelwa
  51,13,Usuku abayovivinywa ngalo emlilweni
  51,14,"Yizwani\tukuvivinywa\tkwenu,\tlokhu\tyilokhu\rnina\renanikusheshisa (nikujaha)"
  51,15,Ngempelaabalungileyobayokubasezivandeninasemithonjeni
  51,16,"Bekuthatha lokho abakunikwa yiNkosi yabo, ngempela bona ngaphambilini kwaloko babengabenzi bokuhle"
  51,17,Babelala kancane ebusuku
  51,18,Futhi entathakusa bona becela intethelelo
  51,19,"Futhi\temnothweni\twabo\tkunesabelo\tsabacelayo nesabangavunyelwe"
  51,20,Futhi emhlabeni kunezimpawu kulabo abaqinisekile
  51,21,Futhi nasemiphefumulweni yenu ngakube aniboni yini na
  51,22,Futhi ezulwini kunesabelo senu kanye nalokho enethenjiswa kona
  51,23,"Ngakho-ke ngeNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, ngempela kona kuyiqiniso njengoba nina nikhuluma"
  51,24,Ngakubeyafikayinikuwenaindabayezivakashiezihloniphekile zika-Abrahamu
  51,25,"Khumbula ngenkathi zifika kuyena zathi, “ukuthula” (u-Abrahamu) wathi, “ukuthula, niyibantu abangaziwa (kumina)”"
  51,26,Wayesephendukela emndenini wakhe wayeseletha inkonyane elinonile
  51,27,"Wayeselibeka eduzane nazo (izivakashi) wathi, “angeke yini nidle?”"
  51,28,"Wayesengenwa ukuzesaba zathi, “ungesabi” zabe sezimnika izindaba ezimnandi ngendodana enolwazi"
  51,29,"Ngakho-ke unkosikazi wakhe weza esho ngezwi elikhulu buhwaqabele ubuso bakhe washo, “(unkosikazi) omdala oyinyumba!”"
  51,30,"Zathi, “isho kanjalo iNkosi yakho ngempela yona inobuhlakani ingeyaziyo”"
  51,31,"Wathi (u-Abrahamu), “iyini inkulumo yenu Oh zithunywa?”"
  51,32,"Zathi, “ngempela thina sithunywe kubantu abayizoni”"
  51,33,Ukuze sithumele phezulu kwabo amatshe obumba
  51,34,Enziwe yiNkosi yakho iwenzela abonayo
  51,35,Ngakho-ke sabakhipha lapho phakathi abakholwayo
  51,36,Kepha asizange sithole lutho lapho phakathi ngaphandle kwendlu yamaMuslim
  51,37,Futhi sashiya lapho phakathi uphawu lalabo abesaba isijeziso esibuhlungu
  51,38,Futhi nakuMose khumbula ngenkathi simthumela kuFaro negunya elicacile
  51,39,"Kepha wafulathela (uFaro) kanye nabalandeli bakhe wayesethi, “umlumbi noma uhlanya!”"
  51,40,Ngakho-ke samthatha kanye namabutho akhe sabaphonsa olwandle futhi nguyena owayefanelwe ukusolwa
  51,41,Futhi naku’AD khumbula ngenkathi sithumela kubona umoya oyinyumba
  51,42,"(Umoya) awuyekanga lutho lokho oweza kukona, kepha wakwenza kwaba sengathi yizingcezu zembubhiso"
  51,43,Futhi nakuThamud khumbula ngenkathi kuthiwa kubona zithokoziseni okwesikhashana
  51,44,"Kepha\tbayidelela\timpoqo\tyeNkosi\tyabo\tngakho-ke kwabathatha ukushaya konyazi kulapho bona bebhekile"
  51,45,Ngakho-ke abazange bakwazi ukuvuka bame noma ukuzisiza
  51,46,"Kanye nabantu baNowa ngaphambilini, ngempela bona babengabantu ababedelela bengahloniphi"
  51,47,Nezulusalakhangezandlafuthingempelathinasingabandisayo
  51,48,"Futhi umhlaba sawendlala, singabalungisi (abandlali) abahle kakhulu"
  51,49,Futhi kuzona zonke izinto sadala kwaba ngambili ukuze nikhumbule
  51,50,Ngakho-ke balekelani kuMvelinqangi ngempela mina kunina ngingumxwayisi ocacile ovela kuyena
  51,51,"Futhi ningahlanganisi noMvelinqangi omunye unkulunkulu, ngempela mina kunina ngingumxwayisi ocacile ovela kuyena"
  51,52,"Kanjalo akuzange kufike kulabo ababengaphambilini kwabo isithunywa ngaphandle kokuthi bathi, “umlumbi noma uhlanya”"
  51,53,"Ngakube babelana ngako njengefa, kepha bona bangabantu abanephutha (abonayo)"
  51,54,"Ngakho-ke bafulathele (suka kubona), wena awusiyena ofanelwe ukusolwa"
  51,55,Futhi khumbuza ngoba ngempela ukukhumbuza kuyabazuzisa abakholwayo
  51,56,Futhi angizange ngidale amajinn(imimoya) nabantu ngaphandle kokuthi bangikhonze
  51,57,Angisifuni kubona isabelo futhi angifuni ukuthi bangondle
  51,58,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi nguyena onika isabelo, umnikazi wamandla oqatha"
  51,59,"Futhi ngempela okwalabo abenza okubi yingxenye efana nengxenye yabangane babo, ngakho-ke abangangiceli ukuthi ngisheshise"
  51,60,Futhi usizi kulabo abangakholwanga osukwini labo abathenjiswa lona
  52,1,Ngifunga ngentaba
  52,2,Ngifunga nencwadi elotshiwe
  52,3,Ekhasini elivulekile
  52,4,Ngifunga nangendlu yokukhonzela (izingelosi)
  52,5,Ngifunga nangophahla oluphakanyisiwe
  52,6,Ngifunga nangolwandle olugcwele luphuphuma
  52,7,Ngempela isijeziso seNkosi yakho sizokwenzeka
  52,8,Akekho ongasivimba
  52,9,"Khumbula\tusuku\tlapho\tizulu\tliyobe\tlizamazama ngokuzamazama (okunamandla)"
  52,10,Futhi izintaba ziyogudluka ukugudluka (okubi) ziyodilika zibe wuthuli
  52,11,Ngakho-ke usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  52,12,"Labo, bona abadlalayo enkulumweni"
  52,13,Ngosuku abayolethwa ngalo emlilweni wesihogo belethwa ngokuphoqwa
  52,14,Lona ngumlilo nina enanijwayele ukuwuphika
  52,15,"Ngakube umlingo yini lona, noma nina aniboni yini na"
  52,16,"Ngenani kusona (isihogo) noma ngabe niyabekezela noma anibekezeli kuyefana kunina, kuphela ninikwa umvuzo walokho nina enanikwenza"
  52,17,Ngempela abalungileyo bayokuba sezivandeni nasenjabulweni
  52,18,Bethokoza ngenxa yalokho abakunikwa yiNkosi yabo futhi yabasindisa iNkosi yabo esijezisweni somlilo ovuthayo
  52,19,Yidlani futhi niphuze ngenjabulo ngenxa yalokho nina enanikwenza
  52,20,Bacambalale emibhedeni engolayini (ekelile) futhi sibashadise nabesifazane abahle abanamehlo amakhulu amahle
  52,21,"Futhi labo abakholwayo futhi balandelwe yinzalo yabo ngokukholwa, siyoyihlanganisa nabo inzalo yabo futhi angeke sibanciphisele ngalutho ezenzweni zabo, bonke abantu banesethembiso ngalokho abakusebenzele"
  52,22,"Futhi\tsiyobandisela\tezithelweni\tnasenyameni\tkulokho abakufisayo"
  52,23,"Lapho bayonikezana inkomishi, angeke ibekhona lapho inkulumo embi futhi akukho ukwenza isono"
  52,24,"Futhibayobazungelezaabafana(kwenzelwa) bona, okusengathi bona bawubuhlalu obulondoloziwe"
  52,25,Futhi abanye babo bayosondela kwabanye bebuzana
  52,26,"Bethi, “ngempela thina ngaphambilini kubantu bethu sasesaba”"
  52,27,Kepha uMvelinqangi wabanomusa kuthina futhi wasisindisa esijezisweni somlilo
  52,28,"Ngempela thina ngaphambilini sasibiza yena, ngempela nguyena omnene onesihawu"
  52,29,Ngakho-ke khumbuza ngobubele beNkosi yakho wena awusisona isangoma noma uhlanya
  52,30,"Noma ngakube bathi, “imbongi silindele ngayo isehlakalo sesikhathi”"
  52,31,"Ithi, “lindani ngakho-ke ngempela mina ngikanye nani kwabalindileyo”"
  52,32,"Noma ngakube baphoqwa yimiqondo yabo ngalokhu, noma bona bangabantu abephula umthetho"
  52,33,"Noma bathi uyenzile, kepha bona abakholwa"
  52,34,Abalethe inkulumo efana nayo uma kungukuthi baneqiniso
  52,35,Noma abazange badalwe ngalutho (yilutho) noma bona uqobo bangabadali
  52,36,Noma ngakube bawadala amazulu nomhlaba? Kepha abaqinisekile
  52,37,Noma ngakube baneminotho yeNkosi yakho noma bona bangabaphathi (beminotho)
  52,38,Noma ngakube banaso yini isitebhisi abezwa ngaso? Manjalo akeze umlaleli wabo negunya elicacile
  52,39,Noma ngakube okwakhe amadodakazi kulapho okwenu kungamadodana
  52,40,Noma ngakube ubacela umvuzo ukuze basindwe yizikweletu
  52,41,Noma ngakube banokungabonwa bona abakuloba phansi na
  52,42,Noma ngakube bafuna ukwenza icebo? Kepha labo abangakholwanga yibona abangabenzi bamacebo
  52,43,Noma ngakube (banomunnye) unkulunkulu okungasiyena uMvelinqangi? Udumo malube kuMvelinqangi ngaphezulu kwalokho abamenzela ngakho abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni
  52,44,"Futhi uma babengayibona ingxenye yesibhakabhaka iwa babezothi, “amafu anqwabelene ndawonye”"
  52,45,Ngakho-ke bayeke kuze kube bahlangana nosuku lwabo abayoshawa ngalo
  52,46,Usuku lapho lingeke libasize ngalutho icebo labo futhi bona angeke balekelelwe
  52,47,Futhi ngempela okwalabo abenza okungalungile yisijeziso okungeyisona leso (kukhona esinye isijeziso ngaphandle kwaleso) kepha iningi labo alazi
  52,48,Futhi (silindile) ngokubekezela isinqumo seNkosi yakho ngokuba ngempela wena usemehlweni ethu futhi phakamisani indumiso yeNkosi yakho uma uvuka
  52,49,Nasebusuku yidumise (iNkosi yakho) nasekusitheleni kwezinkanyezi
  53,1,Ngenkanyezi uma yehla
  53,2,Akazange aduke umngane wenu futhi akazange aphambuke
  53,3,Futhi akakhulumi ngokuthanda (kwakhe)
  53,4,Akuyilutho ngaphandle kwesambulo esambuliwe
  53,5,Wafundiswa onzima onamandla (ingelosi uGabriyeli)
  53,6,"Enamandla amakhulu, manjalo yama yaqonda (ingelosi)"
  53,7,Futhi yona yayisemkhathini iphakeme kakhulu
  53,8,Yabe seyiyasondela yeza eduzane
  53,9,Futhi kwaba yibanga elingangemicibisholo emibili noma okuseduze (kunalokho)
  53,10,"Ngakho-ke\t(iNkosi)\tyembula\tencekwini\tyakhe\tlokho eyakwembula"
  53,11,Inhliziyo ayizange iwaqambe amanga ngalokho eyakubona
  53,12,Ngakube niyaphikisana naye kulokho akubona na
  53,13,Futhi ngempela wayibona (ingelosi) kwesinye isambulo
  53,14,Eduzane nesihlahla somlothi ngasekugcineni komkhawulo
  53,15,Eduze kwayo kunesivande sokuphumula (izulu)
  53,16,Ngenkathi kumboza isidra loko okumbozayo
  53,17,Akuzange kuphambuke ukubona futhi akuzange kuphule umthetho
  53,18,Ngempela wabona okwezimpawu zeNkosi yakhe ezinkulu
  53,19,Ngakube nimbonile yini ullata kanye no uzza
  53,20,Kanye noManat esinye (isithixo) sesithathu
  53,21,Ngakube okwenu abesilisa abakhe abesifazane na
  53,22,Lokho ukwahlukana okungenabo ubulungiswa
  53,23,"Aziyilutho (izithixo) ngaphandle kwamagama eniwaqambe zona, nina kanye naboyihlo, okungukuthi uMvelinqangi akalehliselanga phansi igunya ngako, abalandeli ngaphandle komcabango kanye nalokho okufiswa yimiphefumulo, futhi ngempela kwabafikela ukuholwa okuvela eNkosini yabo"
  53,24,Noma ngakube okomuntu yilokho akufisayo
  53,25,Kepha kungokukaMvelinqangi okokugcina (impilo ezayo) nokokuqala (impilo yalomhlaba)
  53,26,Futhi zingaki izingelosi ezisemazulwini okungasizi ngalutho ukuncenga kwazo ngaphandle kwangemumva kokuba uma uMvelinqangi evumela lowo amthandayo namthokozelayo
  53,27,Ngempela labo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo baqamba izingelosi ngamagama abesifazane
  53,28,"Futhi abanalo ulwazi ngako (lokho abakushoyo), abalandeli lutho ngaphandle komcabango futhi ngempela umcabango awuzuzi lutho eqinisweni"
  53,29,Ngakho-ke qhelelana nalowo ofulathela isikhumbuzo sethu futhi ongathandi ngaphandle kwempilo yalomhlaba
  53,30,"Lokho yisamba sabo solwazi, ngempela iNkosi yakho yona yazi kangcono ngalowo ophambukile endleleni yayo futhi yona yazi kangcono ngalowo oholeleke (endleleni eqondile)"
  53,31,Futhi ngokukaMvelinqangi konke okusemazulwini nakho konke okusemhlabeni ukuze anikeze umvuzo labo abenza okubi ngalokho abakwenzayo futhi anikeze umvuzo labo abenza okuhle kakhulu ngokuhle
  53,32,"Labo abagwema izono ezinkulu kanye nemikhuba ngaphandle kwamaphutha amancane, ngempela iNkosi yakho inentethelelo ebanzi, yona yazi kabanzi ngani ngenkathi iniveza emhlabeni nangenkathi nina niseyizingane ezingakazalwa eziswini zonyoko, ngakho-ke ningayiphi imiphefumulo yenu ubumsulwa yena wazi kakhulu ngalowo owesaba (uMvelinqangi nogwema okubi futhi olungileyo)"
  53,33,Ngakube umbonile yini lowo owafulathela
  53,34,Futhi wapha kancane wabe eseyayeka
  53,35,Ngakube unalo yini ulwazi lokungabonwa ukuze yena abone
  53,36,Noma akazange yini atshelwe ngalokho okusemibhalweni kaMose
  53,37,Kanye no-Abrahamu owayegcwalisekisa (lokho okudingekayo kuyena)
  53,38,Ukuthi akekho umthwali wemithwalo oyothwala umthwalo womunye
  53,39,Futhi akukho okomuntu ngaphandle kwalokho akwenzayo
  53,40,Futhi imisebenzi yakhe iyobonakala
  53,41,"Bese (uMvelinqangi) emnika umvuzo, umvuzo ogcwele"
  53,42,Futhi iseNkosini yakho lapho kuyisiphetho khona
  53,43,Futhi iyona eyenza ukuhleka nokukhala
  53,44,Futhi iyona edala ukufa nenika impilo
  53,45,"Nokuthi yadala ngakubili, isilisa nesifazane"
  53,46,Ngesidoda uma sikhishwa
  53,47,Futhi kuyena (uMvelinqangi) kunokunye ukuvezwa (indalo noma ukuvuswa kwabafileyo)
  53,48,Nokuthi nguyena ophanayo (ngomnotho) nokwaneliseka
  53,49,Nokuthi yena (uMvelinqangi) uyiNkosi ye-As’shiri (inkanyezi eyayikhonzwa yingxenye yama-Arab)
  53,50,Nokuthi yona yabhubhisa i-A’D yokuqala
  53,51,"NeThamud\t(abantu\tbaseThamud)\takazange\tabashiye (wababhubhisa)"
  53,52,"Kanye nabantu baNowa (babhujiswa) ngaphambilini, ngempela bona babengenabo ubulungiswa ngokudlulele futhi bephula umthetho ngokudlulele"
  53,53,Futhi wabhubhisa amadolobha agumbukeqiswa phansi
  53,54,Ngakho-ke (amadolobha) ambozwa yilokho akwambozwa
  53,55,Ngakho-ke yikuphi kobubele beNkosi yakho okungabazayo na
  53,56,Lona ngumxwayisi wabaxwayisi bakudala (basemandulo)
  53,57,Usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo luyasondela
  53,58,Akekho namunye ongalivimba ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi
  53,59,Ngakube niyamangala yini kulenkulumo na
  53,60,Futhi niyahleka anikhali
  53,61,Kulapho nina nizijabulisa
  53,62,Ngakho-ke guqelani uMvelinqangi futhi nimkhonze
  54,1,Ihora liyasondela nenyanga yahlephuka phakathi
  54,2,"Futhi uma bebona uphawu bayafulathela futhi bathi, “(lona) ngumlingo oqhubekayo”"
  54,3,"Futhi baziphika (izimpawu zikaMvelinqangi) base belandela izinkanuko zabo, kepha zonke izindaba ziyohlelwa (uma sekufika isikhathi sazo)"
  54,4,Futhi ngempela sezafika kubona izindaba ezixwayisayo nezinezifundo
  54,5,"Ubuhlakani obuhle, kepha (ukushumayela) kwabaxwayisi akuzange kubasize"
  54,6,"Ngakho-ke qhelelana nabo, bese ukhumbule usuku lapho ummemi eyomemela entweni embi kakhulu (esabisayo)"
  54,7,"Amehlo abo ezithobile, bephuma emangcwabeni kube sengathi bona bayizintethe ezisakazekile"
  54,8,"Bejahe kummemezi abangakholwanga bethi, “lolu wusuku olunzima”"
  54,9,Ngaphambilini kwabo abantu baNowa bayiphika inceku yethu futhi bathi “uhlanya” yagxoshwa
  54,10,Ngakho-ke (inceku yethu) yabiza iNkosi yayo (yathi) “nginqotshiwe ngakho-ke ngisize
  54,11,Ngakho-ke sawavula amasango ezulu ngamanzi amaningi
  54,12,Futhi sawenza umhlaba ukuthi uqhekeke ngemithombo ngakho-ke amanzi ahlanganela udaba olwaselunqunyiwe ngaphambilini
  54,13,Futhi samthwala (uNowa ngomkhumbi) owakhiwe ngamapulangwe kanye nezipikili
  54,14,"Untanta ngaphansi kwamehlo ethu, umvuzo walowo owayephikwa"
  54,15,"Futhi ngempela sakushiya (lokho) ukuthi kube wuphawu, ngakho-ke ngakube ukhona yini oyokhumbula"
  54,16,"Manjalo, sasinjani isijeziso sami nesexwayiso sami"
  54,17,Futhi ngempela sayenza iQur’an yabalula ukuze ikhumbuleke ngakho-ke ngakube ukhona yini ozokhumbula
  54,18,Waphika u-AD kepha sasinjani isijeziso sami nesexwayiso sami
  54,19,Ngempela thina sawuthumela umoya oyisibhengubhengu ngosuku lwesehlakalo esiqhubekayo
  54,20,(Umoya) ukhipha abantu kube sengathi bona bayiziqu zemithi yesundu esimbuliwe
  54,21,Manjalo sasinjani isijeziso sami kanye nesexwayiso sami
  54,22,Futhi ngempela sayenza iQur’an yabalula ukuthi ikhumbuleke ngakube ukhona yini okhumbulayo
  54,23,UThamud waziphika izexwayiso
  54,24,"Kepha bathi, “ngakube umuntu oyedwa ophuma phakathi kwethu simlandele? Ngempela thina ngabe sisekudukeni nasekuhlanyeni”"
  54,25,"Ngakube sesathunyelwa yini kuyena isikhumbuzo esivela phakathi kwethu, kepha yena ungumqambi wamanga ozigabisayo"
  54,26,Bazokwazi kusasa ukuthi ngubani ongumqambi wamanga ozigabisayo
  54,27,Ngempela sithumela ikameli lensikazi njengesilingo kubona ngakho-ke babuke futhi ubekezele
  54,28,"Futhi batshene ukuthi amanzi azohlukaniswa phakathi kwabo, konke ukuphuza kwabo kwenziwe"
  54,29,"Kepha\tbamemeza\tabakanye\tnabo\t(abangane\tbabo) wayesethatha (inkemba) wayeselibulala (ikameli lensikazi)"
  54,30,Manjalo sasinjani isijeziso sami kanye nesexwayiso sami
  54,31,Futhi ngempela sawuthumela kubona umsindo owesabekayo owodwa babe sebeba njengoluthi olomile
  54,32,Futhi ngempela sayenza iQur’an yabalula ukuze ikhumbuleke ngakube ukhona yini okhumbulayo
  54,33,Abantu baLothi baziphika izexwayiso
  54,34,Ngempela sathumela kubona isichotho samatshe esinamandla ngaphandle komndeni kaLothi sabaphephisa entathakusa
  54,35,"Umusa ovela kuthina, kanjalo simnika umvuzo lowo obongayo"
  54,36,Futhi ngempela wabaxwayisa ngokushaya kwethu (ngesijeziso sethu) kepha abazethembanga izexwayiso
  54,37,Futhi ngempela baphoqa kuyena izivakashi zakhe manjalo sawavala amehlo abo (sathi) “yizwani isijeziso sami kanye nezexwayiso zami”
  54,38,"Futhi\tngempela\tbavuka\tekuseni\tngesijeziso\tesingasuki (esingapheli)"
  54,39,Ngakho-ke yizwani isijeziso sami kanye nezexwayiso
  54,40,"Futhi ngempela sayenza iQur’an yabalula ukuze ikhumbuleke, ngakube ukhona yini okhumbulayo na"
  54,41,Futhi ngempela bafika kubantu baFaro abaxwayisi
  54,42,"Baziphika izimpawu zethu zonke, manjalo sababamba ngokubamba kophakeme ngamandla okwaziyo (ukwenza zonke izinto)"
  54,43,Ngakube abangakholwa benu bangcono kunabo noma abanacala ezincwadini (emibhalweni)
  54,44,"Noma ngakube bathi, “thina sihlangene siyalekelelana”"
  54,45,Ibutho (labo) liyohlulwa bese beyafulathela beveza imihlane (yabo)
  54,46,"Kepha ihora yisethembiso sabo, futhi ihora liyobanzima kakhulu futhi liyobamuncu kakhulu"
  54,47,Ngempela abayizoni basekudukeni nasekuhlanyeni
  54,48,"Khumbula ngosuku lapho beyodonselwa emlilweni ngobuso babo, kuyothiwa yizwani ukuthintwa yisihogo"
  54,49,Ngempela zonke izinto sazidala ngesilinganiso
  54,50,Futhi impoqo yethu ayiyilutho ngaphandle kokucwazima kweso okukodwa
  54,51,Futhi ngempela sababhubhisa abafana nani ngakho-ke ngakube ukhona yini okhumbulayo na
  54,52,Futhi zonke izinto abazenzayo zishicilelwe kwiZubur (incwadi ekushicilelwa kuyona izenzo zabo)
  54,53,Futhi konke okuncane nokukhulu kushicilelwe phansi (kulotshiwe)
  54,54,Ngempela abalungileyo bayokuba sezivandeni nasemifuleni
  54,55,Esihlalweni seqiniso eduzane neNkosi enkulu eyenza (zonke izinto)
  55,1,(UMvelinqangi) onomusa
  55,2,Wafundisa iQur’an
  55,3,Wadala umuntu
  55,4,Wamfundisa ukukhuluma
  55,5,Ilanga nenyanga kuhamba ngendlela ekuyiyona ngasosonke isikhathi
  55,6,Futhi izinkanyezi kanye nezihlahla kokubili (kukhothamela umthetho kaMvelinqangi)
  55,7,Nezulu waliphakamisa wayesebeka isikalo
  55,8,Ukuze ningoni esikalini
  55,9,"Futhi niqaphele isisindo ngobulungiswa, futhi ningasinciphisi isilinganiso"
  55,10,Futhi umhlaba wawubekela izidalwa
  55,11,"Lapho phakathi kukhona izithelo, nezihlahla zamasundu ezinezixheke"
  55,12,"Nohlamvu\tkanye\tnoluthi\tolomile\tlukakolweni\t(noma amaqabunga aluhlaza) kanye nezihlahla ezinuka amakha"
  55,13,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,14,"Wadala\tumuntu\tngobumba\tolunjengolokwakha\tizitsha zobumba"
  55,15,Futhi wadala amajinn ngelangabi lomlilo
  55,16,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,17,INkosi yezimpumalanga ezimbili neNkosi yezintshonalanga ezimbili
  55,18,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,19,Yenza ukuthi izilwandle ezimbili zihlangane
  55,20,Phakathi kwazo zombili (izilwandle) kunomngcele zombili ezingaweqi
  55,21,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,22,"Kuzona zombili kuphuma ubuhlalu, ubuhlalu obukhulu nobuncane"
  55,23,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,24,Futhi ngeyakhe imikhumbi ehamba olwandle ephakeme njengezintaba
  55,25,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,26,Bonke abaphezulu kwawo (umhlaba) bayobhubha
  55,27,Kepha kuyosala ubuso beNkosi yakho umnikazi wobukhosi ohloniphekile
  55,28,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,29,"Bacela\tyena\t(uMvelinqangi)\tbonke\tabasemazulwini nasemhlabeni, zonke izinsuku yena usodabeni"
  55,30,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,31,Siyoninaka (siyonehlulela) Oh Nina maqembu amabili! (abantu namajinn)
  55,32,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,33,"Oh Sixuku samajinn nabantu! Uma nikwazi ukuthi nedlule ngaphambili kwezindawo zamazulu nomhlaba ngakho-ke dlulani, angeke nedlule ngaphandle kwegunya"
  55,34,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,35,"Kuyothunyelwa kunina nobabili amalangabi omlilo kanye nentuthu, manjalo angeke nikwazi ukuzivikela nobabili"
  55,36,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,37,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tizulu\tliyohlukana\tphakathi\tlibe yimibalabala eshintshayo"
  55,38,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,39,"Manjalo, ngalolosuku angeke abuzwe ngesono sakhe umuntu nejinn angeke libuzwe ngesono salo"
  55,40,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,41,"Bayokwaziwa\tabayizoni\tngezimpawu\tzabo\tngakho-ke bayobanjwa ngeziphongo nangezinyawo (zabo)"
  55,42,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,43,Lesi yisihogo ababesiphika abayizoni
  55,44,Bayojikeleza phakathi kwaso naphakathi kwamanzi abilayo
  55,45,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,46,Kepha okwalowo owesaba ukuma kweNkosi yakhe (ukuze imehlulele) yizivande ezimbili
  55,47,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,48,Zombili (izivande imithi yazo) inamagatsha
  55,49,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,50,Phakathi kuzona kunemithombo emibili egijimayo
  55,51,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,52,Phakathi kuzona zombili (izivande) kukhona zonke izithelo ngambili
  55,53,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,54,Becambalele emibhedeni izembozo (izingubo) zayo ziwusilika onohlonze futhi izithelo zezivande ezimbili ziseduze
  55,55,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,56,"Phakathi kuzona zombili (izivande) kunabesifazane abamsulwa ababheka ngokuzotha, abangakaze bathintwe abantu ngaphambilini kwabo futhi (abangakaze) bathintwe amajinn"
  55,57,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,58,Okusengathi bona bangamaRubhi nobuhlalu
  55,59,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,60,Ngakube ukhona yini umvuzo wokuhle ngaphandle kokuhle
  55,61,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,62,Futhi ngaphandle (kwezivande) ezimbili kunezivande ezimbili ezinye
  55,63,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,64,Zombili ziluhlaza okumnyama
  55,65,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,66,Phakathi kuzona zombili (izivande) kunemithombo emibili ephophozayo
  55,67,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,68,Phakathi kuzona zombili kunezithelo nezihlahla zamasundu namahalananda (uhlobo lwesithelo esinezinhlamvu eziningi)
  55,69,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,70,Phakathi kuzona kunezinto ezinhle ezilungile
  55,71,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,72,Abesifazane abahle ababekwe ematendeni amakhulu
  55,73,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,74,(Abesifazane) abangakaze bathintwe ngabantu ngaphambilini kwabo futhi abangakaze (bathintwe amajinn)
  55,75,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,76,Becambalele emaphilweni aluhlaza kanye nakokhaphethi abahle
  55,77,Ngakho-ke yikuphi komusa weNkosi yenu nobabili (abantu namajinn) enikuphikayo
  55,78,"Alibusiswe igama leNkosi yakho umnikazi wobukhosi, kanye nodumo. likaMvelinqangi onomusa onesihawu"
  56,1,Khumbula uma isehlakalo sehlakala
  56,2,Akusiwona amanga ukwehlakala kwaso
  56,3,Sehlisa (abanye) siphakamisa (abanye)
  56,4,Khumbula lapho umhlaba unyakaziswa ngokuzamazama
  56,5,Nezintaba zibhidlizwa ziba wuthuli
  56,6,Bese zibawuthuli olusaphazekile
  56,7,Futhi naniyizigaba ezintathu
  56,8,"Manjalo\tabangane\tbangakwesokudla,\tyini\tabangane bangakwesokudla"
  56,9,"Kanye\tnabangane\tbangakwesobunxele,\tyini\tabangane bangakwesobunxele"
  56,10,"Nabedlulelayo\t(ekwenzeni\tizenzo\tezinhle\tkulomhlaba) bangabedlulelayo (empilweni ezayo)"
  56,11,Labo bangabasondele (kuMvelinqangi)
  56,12,Bayongena ezivandeni zentokozo
  56,13,Isixuku sabantu basendulo
  56,14,Kanye nabambalwa kwabangamumva
  56,15,Emibhedeni ephothwe ngegolide
  56,16,Becambalele phezulu kwayo bebhekene
  56,17,Bayobazungeleza abafana bangunaphakade
  56,18,"Nezinkomishi,\tnabojeke\tkanye\tnezingilazi\tzewayini eligobhozayo"
  56,19,Alibaphathisi ngekhanda futhi alibashintshi umqondo
  56,20,Kanye nezithelo abakhetha kuzona
  56,21,Kanye nenyama yezinkukhu abayithandayo
  56,22,Kanye nabesifazane abamhlophe abanamehlo amakhulu amahle
  56,23,Abafana njengobuhlalu obugciniwe
  56,24,Umvuzo ngenxa yalokho ababekwenza
  56,25,Abayizwa lapho phakathi inkulumo eyize noma ukwenza isono
  56,26,"Ngaphandle kwesisho, “ukuthula! Ukuthula!”"
  56,27,"Futhi\tabangane\tbangakwesokudla\t–\tyini\tabangane bangakwesokudla"
  56,28,Bayoba sezihlahleni zomlothi ezingenawo ameva
  56,29,Nezihlahlai ezinezixheke (zezithelo)
  56,30,Kanye nomthunzi owandisiwe (obanzi)
  56,31,Kanye namanzi agobhozayo
  56,32,Kanye nezithelo eziningi
  56,33,Akunqamuki(ukubakhonakwazoizithelo) futhiazenqatshelwe (zitholakala kalula)
  56,34,Nemibhede ephakanyisiwe
  56,35,Ngempela thina (sabadala abesifazane basezulwini) ngendalo
  56,36,Futhi sabenza baba ngabesifazane abamsulwa abangakaze bathintwe
  56,37,Banothando bayalingana ngeminyaka
  56,38,Okwalabo abangakwesokudla
  56,39,Iqembu labantu basendulo
  56,40,Kanye neqembu langamumva
  56,41,"Futhi labo abangasesandleni sobunxele, yini abangane abangakwesobunxele"
  56,42,Bayongena emlilweni oshisayo nasemanzini abilayo
  56,43,Kanye nethunzi lentuthu emnyama
  56,44,Elingapholile futhi elingajabulisi
  56,45,Ngempela bona ngaphambilini kwalokho babephila impilo entofontofo
  56,46,Futhi babephikelela ezonweni ezinkulu
  56,47,"Futhi babethi, “ngakube uma sesifile sabawuthuli namathambo ngempela siyobuye sivuswe kwabafileyo?”"
  56,48,Kanye nabokhokho bethu
  56,49,"Ithi, “ngempela (bayovuswa kwabafileyo) abasemandulo kanye nabangamumva”"
  56,50,Ngempela bayoqoqelwa ndawonye (beqoqelwa) isikhathi sosuku olwaziwayo
  56,51,"Manjalo, ngempela Oh Nina abaphambukayo abaphikayo"
  56,52,Ngempela nizodla esihlahleni sezaqum
  56,53,"Manjalo, nigcwalise izisu (zenu) ngaso"
  56,54,Bese niphuza phezulu kwaso amanzi abilayo
  56,55,Niphuze njengokuphuza kwekameli elomile
  56,56,Lokhu ukujatshuliswa kwabo ngosuku lokwahlulelwa
  56,57,"Thina sanidala, ngakho-ke kungani ningakholwa"
  56,58,Ngakube nikubonile yini lokho enikukhiphayo (ubudoda)
  56,59,Ngakube yinina yini enikudalile noma yithina umdali
  56,60,Thina sakwenza ukufa phakathi kwenu futhi thina asedlulwa
  56,61,Ukuthi sikuguqule ukufana kwenu (silethe enye indalo esikhundleni senu) futhi sinidale nibe yilokho eningakwazi
  56,62,Futhi ngempela senikwazile ukudalwa kokuqala manjalo kungani ningakhumbuli
  56,63,Ngakube nikubonile yini lokho enikutshalayo
  56,64,Ngakube yinina enikwenza ukuthi kumile (kukhule) noma yithina ummilisi
  56,65,"Ukube besithanda, besizokwenza kube wuthuli bese nina niyamangala (niyazisola)"
  56,66,Ngempela thina sisesikweletini
  56,67,Kepha thina siphuciwe
  56,68,Ngakube niwabonile yini amanzi eniwaphuzayo
  56,69,Ngakube yinina yini eniwahlisele phansi ephuma emafini noma yithina umehliseli phansi
  56,70,Ukube besithanda besizowenza abeduma (angaphuzeki) manjalo kungani ningabongi
  56,71,Ngakube niwubonile yini umlilo eniwokhelayo
  56,72,Ngakube yinina yini enenza ukuthi kukhule izihlahla zawo (umhlaba) noma yithina umkhulisi
  56,73,Thina sawenza waba yisikhumbuzo kanye nosizo ezihlalini zasogwadule
  56,74,Ngakho-ke dumisa igama leNkosi yakho enkulu kakhulu
  56,75,Manjalo ngifunga ngokubekwa kwezinkanyezi
  56,76,Futhi ngempela yisifungo esikhulu ukube benazi
  56,77,Ngempela yona iyiQur’an ehloniphekile
  56,78,Encwadini elondolozekile
  56,79,Ayithintwa ngaphandle kwabamsulwa
  56,80,Isambulo esivela eNkosini yemihlaba
  56,81,Ngakube yileNkulumo yini nina eningakholelwa kuyona
  56,82,Futhi nenza isabelo senu ukuthi kube ukwenqaba kwenu
  56,83,Manjalo kungani uma (umphefumulo uphuma) ufinyelela emninzweni
  56,84,Futhi nina ngalesosikhathi nibhekile
  56,85,Futhi thina siseduzane kakhulu kuyena kunani kepha aniboni
  56,86,Manjalo kungani ningenzi – uma kungukuthi nina angeke nehlulelwe
  56,87,Wubuyiseleni emumvaumakungukuthininaningabaneqiniso
  56,88,Manjalo uma wayengomunye wabasondezwe eduzane
  56,89,Manjalo ukuphumula nezabelo kanye nesivande senjabulo
  56,90,Futhi uma engomunye wabangane bangakwesokunene
  56,91,"Ngakho-ke\tukuthula\tkungokwakho\tongowabangane bangakwesokunene"
  56,92,Futhi uma wayengomunye wabaphikayo abaphambukayo (eqinisweni)
  56,93,Manjalo ukujatshuliswa (kwakhe) amanzi abilayo
  56,94,Nokusha emlilweni wesihogo
  56,95,Ngempela lokhu yiqiniso langempela
  56,96,"Ngakho-ke dumisa igama leNkosi yakho, enkulu"
  57,1,KudumisauMvelinqangikonkeokusemazulwininasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  57,2,Ungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba uyaphilisa futhi uyabulala futhi yena wenza zonke izinto
  57,3,Yena ungowokuqala nowokugcina nosobala nosithele futhi yena uyisazi sazozonke izinto
  57,4,"Nguyena owadala amazulu nomhlaba ezinsukwini eziyisithupha wayesezibeka esihlalweni sobukhosi, wazi konke okungena emhlabeni nakho konke okuphuma kuwona kanye nakho konke okwehlela phansi okuphuma ezulwini nakho konke okunyukela khona futhi yena ukanye nani noma ngabe yikuphi lapho nikhona futhi uMvelinqangi uyakubona lokho enikwenzayo"
  57,5,Ungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi ikuMvelinqangi lapho zibuyiselwa khona izindaba
  57,6,Wenza ukuthi ubusuku bungenele emini futhi wenza ukuthi imini ingenele ebusuku futhi yena uyakwazi lokho okusezifubeni
  57,7,"Kholwani kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi nisebenzise kulokho anenza naba abalandelayo kukona, kepha labo abakholwayo phakathi kwenu futhi abasebenzisayo (abanikelayo) okwabo ngumvuzo omkhulu"
  57,8,Futhi kungani ningakholelwa kuMvelinqangi kanti isithunywa sinimemela ekukholelweni eNkosini yenu futhi yasithatha isivumelwano senu uma kungukuthi nina ningamakholwa
  57,9,Yena uyilowo owehlisela phezulu kwenceku yakhe amavesi acacile ukuze anikhiphe ebumnyameni aniyise ekukhanyeni futhi ngempela uMvelinqangi ngani umnene unesihawu
  57,10,"Futhi kungani ningasebenzisi endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi ngelikaMvelinqangi ifa lamazulu nomhlaba abalingani phakathi kwenu laba abasebenzisa ngaphambili kokunqoba futhi balwa, labo bakhulu kakhulu ngezinga kunalabo abasebenzisa ngamumva futhi balwa, futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo"
  57,11,Ngubani lowo ongaboleka uMvelinqangi ukuboleka okuhle ukuzeamphindelekonakabilibeseebanomvuzoohloniphekile
  57,12,Khumbula ngosuku uyobona abesilisa abakholwayo nabesifazane abakholwayo ukukhanya kwabo kuhamba ngaphambili kwabo futhi ngakwezokunene zabo izindaba zenu ezinhle namhlanje yizivande okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula bayohlala khona ingunaphakade lokho ukuphumelela okukhulu
  57,13,"Ngosuku lapho abazenzisi besilisa nabazenzisi besifazane beyothi kulabo abakholwayo “silindeni ukuze sithole okokukhanya kwenu” kuyothiwa “phindelani emumva ngemumva kwenu bese nifuna ukukhanya” manjalo kuyobekwa udonga phakathi kwabo olunesango ngaphakathi, ngaphakathi kunomusa kepha ngaphandle kwalo kunesijeziso"
  57,14,"Bayobamemeza (abangakholwanga bathi), “sasingeve yini sikanye nani?” bayothi, “yebo kepha nina naniyilinga imiphefumulo yenu futhi nalinda nangabaza kanye nemicabango eyanikhohlisa kwaze kwafika impoqo kaMvelinqangi futhi wanikhohlisa ngoMvelinqangi umkhohlisi (ongusathane)”"
  57,15,"Manjalo kulolusuku angeke yamukelwe kunina inhlengo futhi angeke (yamukelwe) kulabo abangakholwanga, indawo yenu yokuhlala umlilo wona ungumngane wenu futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona"
  57,16,"Asikafiki yini isikhathi kulabo abakholwayo sokuthi izinhliziyo zabo zithobele isikhumbuzo sikaMvelinqangi kanye nalokho okwehlela phansi okuyiqiniso (okwambuliwe) futhi abangabi njengalabo ababenikezwe incwadi ngaphambilini futhi belulelwa isikhathi, manjalo zabalukhuni izinhliziyo zabo futhi iningi labo izephulamthetho"
  57,17,"Yazini ukuthi uMvelinqangi uphilisa umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo, sazenza zacaca kunina izimpawu ukuze niqonde"
  57,18,Ngempela abesilisa abaneqiniso nabesifazane abaneqiniso futhi baboleka uMvelinqangi ukuboleka okuhle bayophindelwa kabili futhi okwabo ngumvuzo ohloniphekile
  57,19,"Futhi labo abakholwa kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe labo ngabaneqiniso kanye nabafela ukholo baseduzane neNkosi yabo okwabo ngumvuzo wabo kanye nokukhanya kwabo, kepha labo abangakholwa futhi abawaphika amavesi ethu labo bangabangane bomlilo ovuthayo"
  57,20,Yazini ukuthi impilo yalomhlaba ingumdlalo nenjabulo nobuhle nokuzikhukhumeza phakathi kwenu nokuqhudelana mayelana nengcebo nezingane njengemvula okumilayo kwayo kujabulisa abalimi bese kuyoma ukubone kuphenduka kubaphuzi besekubayimfucumfucu futhi empilweni ezayo kunesijeziso esinzima nentethelelo evela kuMvelinqangi nenjabulo futhi ayiyilutho impilo yalomhlaba ngaphandle kwenjabulo eyinkohliso
  57,21,"Ncintisanani entethelelweni evela eNkosini yenu nasesivandeni ububanzi baso bunjengobubanzi bezulu nomhlaba silungiselelwe labo abakholwa kuMvelinqangi nesithumywa sakhe, lowo ngumusa kaMvelinqangi uwunika lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi unomusa omkhulu"
  57,22,"Asikho isenzakalo esenzakalayo emhlabeni ngisho nasemiphefumulweni yenu ngaphandle kokuthi sisencwadini ngaphambili kokuba sisiveze, ngempela lokho kuMvelinqangi kulula"
  57,23,"Ukuze ningabi usizi ngalokho okwaniphunyuka futhi ningajabuli ngalokho aninika kona, futhi uMvelinqangi akabathandi bonke abaziqhenyayo abazigabisayo"
  57,24,"Labo abancishanayo bayalele abantu ngokuncishana futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofulathelayo, manjalo ngempela uMvelinqangi yena akadingi lutho ungodunyiswayo"
  57,25,"Ngempela sazithumela izithunywa zethu namavesi acacile futhi sehlisela phansi kanye nabo incwadi kanye nesilinganiso ukuze abantu benze ubulungiswa futhi sehlisela phansi insimbi kuyona kunamandla amakhulu kanye nezinzuzo zabantu futhi ukuze amazi uMvelinqangi lowo omsizayo (ngokumkhonza) nesithunywa sakhe engabonwa, ngempela uMvelinqangi uqatha, uphakeme ngamandla"
  57,26,Futhi ngempela samthumela uNowa no-Abrahamu futhi sabeka ezizukulwaneni zabo bobabili ubuphrofethi nencwadi manjalo phakathi kwabo kunalabo abaholelekile (endleleni eqondile) kepha iningi labo izephulamthetho
  57,27,"Manjalo sazenza izithunywa zethu ukuthi zilandele ezinyathelweni zabo futhi salandelisa ngoJesu indodana kaMaryam (Mariya) samnika i-Injil (iVangeli) futhi safaka ezinhliziyweni zalabo abamlandela ububele nomusa nobuzindela (ubuRoma) abazenzela bona asibenzelanga bona ngaphandle kokufuna injabulo nomusa kaMvelinqangi, kepha abazange babugcine ngendlela obugcinwa ngayo, ngakho-ke sabanika labo abakholwayo phakathi kwabo umvuzo wabo, kepha iningi labo liyizephulamthetho"
  57,28,"Oh nina enikholwayo! Yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi nikholwe yisithunywa sakhe uzoninika izingxenye ezimbili emseni wakhe bese enibekela ukukhanya enizohamba kukona futhi anithethelele, futhi uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  57,29,Ukuze abantu bencwadi bazi ukuthi abakwazi ukwenza lutho emseni kaMvelinqangi nokuthi umusa usesandleni sikaMvelinqangi uwunika lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi unomusa omkhulu
  58,1,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyizwile inkulumo leyo owesifazane ayephikisana ngayo nawe mayelana nomyeni wakhe, ekhononda kuMvelinqangi futhi uMvelinqangi uyayizwa ingxoxo yenu nobabili ngempela uMvelinqangi ungozwayo obonayo"
  58,2,"Labo phakathi kwenu abenza amakhosikazi abo angabi semthethweni (ngokuwabiza ngokuthi imihlane yawo injengeyonina, lokho babekwenzela isehlukaniso) wona (amakhosikazi abo) akawasibona onina, akuyibona onina ngaphandle kwabesifazane ababazala futhi ngempela bona basho inkulumo embi neyamanga ngempela uMvelinqangi ungoxolelayo othethelelayo"
  58,3,"Futhi labo abathi imihlane yamakhosikazi abo ifana neyabonina bese beyakuhoxisa lokho abakushilo ngakho-ke kufanele kukhululwe isigqila ngaphambili kokuba bathintane, lokho niyayalwa ngako futhi uMvelinqangi lokho enikwenzayo uyakwazi"
  58,4,Ngakho-ke lowo ongasitholi (isigqila azosikhulula) akazile izinyanga ezimbili ezilandelanayo ngaphambili kokuba bathintane ngakho-ke lowo ongakwazi (ukukwenza lokho) ngakho-ke akondle abantu abangamashumi ayisithupha abampofu lokho (kwenzelwa ukuthi) nikholelwe kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi leyo yimingcele kaMvelinqangifuthiokwabangakholwayisijezisoesibuhlungu
  58,5,Ngempela labo abaphikisa uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe bathotshiswa njengokuthotshiswa kwalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo futhi ngempela sawembula amavesi acacile futhi okwabangakholwa yisijeziso esijabhisayo (esidumazayo)
  58,6,"Khumbula ngosuku lapho uMvelinqangi eyobavusa bonke bese ebatshena ngaloko ababekwenza, uMvelinqangi wakubala (konke ababekwenza) kulapho sebekukhohliwe, futhi uMvelinqangi uyazibona zonke izinto"
  58,7,"Awuboni yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi konke okusemazulwini nako konke okusemhlabeni, futhi uMvelinqangi awukho umhlangano wasesithe wabathathu ngaphandle kokuba yena ungowesine futhi akekho owesihlanu ngaphandle kokuba yena ungowesithupha wabo futhi akukho okungaphansi kwalokho noma okungaphezulu ngaphandle kokuthi yena ukanye nabo noma ngabe yikuphi lapho bekhona bese ebatshela ngalokho ababekwenza ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazazi zonke izinto"
  58,8,"Awubaboni yini labo ababenqatshelwe umhlangano wangasese bese bebuyela kuloko ababenqatshelwe kukona bese behlangana ndawonye ngesono nobutha kanye nokungasihloniphi isithunywa, futhi uma befika kuwena bakubingelela ngaloko angakubingeleli ngako uMvelinqangi futhi bathi emiphefumulweni yabo, “kungani engasijezisi uMvelinqangi ngaloko esikushoyo?” sibanele isihogo bayosha kusona kubi lapho kuyiwa khona"
  58,9,Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma nihlangana ngasese ngakho- ke ningahlangani ngasese ngesono nobutha kanye nokungasihloniphi isithunywa kepha yibani nemihlangano yangasese ngokuhle nokwesaba futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi okunguyena eniyoqoqelwa ndawonye kuyena
  58,10,Kuphela izinkulumo zangasese zivela kusathane ukuze enze labo abakholwayo babewusizi futhi angeke balinyazwe yilutho ngaphandle uma kungokwentando kaMvelinqangi futhi ikuMvelinqangi lapho bethembela khona abakholwayo
  58,11,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma kuthiwa kunina “vulani indawo emihlanganweni” ngakho-ke yivuleni uyonivulela indawo uMvelinqangi futhi uma kuthiwa (kunina) “sukumani” ngakho-ke sukumani, uyabaphakamisa uMvelinqangi labo abakholwayo phakathi kwenu kanye nalabo abanikezwa ulwazi ngamazinga futhi uMvelinqangi lokho enikwenzayo uyakwazi"
  58,12,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma nihlangana nesithunywa ngasese ngakho-ke nikelani ngesipho ngaphambili kokuxoxisana kwenu, lokho kungcono kunina futhi kumsulwa kakhulu, kepha uma ningasitholi (isipho) ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  58,13,"Ngakube niyesaba yini ukunikela ngezipho ngaphambili kokuxoxisana kwenu na? Manjalo uma ningakwenzi lokho, uMvelinqangi unithethelele, ngakho-ke yenzani umthandazo ninikeze (nikhokhe) izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi nihloniphe uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi uMvelinqangi uyazi ngaloko enikwenzayo"
  58,14,Awubaboni yini labo abenza ubungane nabantu ubathukuthelele uMvelinqangi abasibona abenu futhi abasibona ababo futhi bafunga ngamanga kulapho bona bazi
  58,15,"UMvelinqangi wabalungiselela isijeziso esinzima, ngempela bona okubi lokho ababekwenza"
  58,16,"Bathatha izifungo zabo njengesisitho, manjalo bavimba (abanye) endleleni kaMvelinqangi, ngakho-ke okwabo yisijeziso esidumazayo"
  58,17,"Ayisoze yabasiza ngalutho ingcebo yabo nezingane zabo kuMvelinqangi, labo-ke yizihlali zomlilo ziyokuba kuwona ingunaphakade"
  58,18,"Ngosuku ayobavusa ngalo uMvelinqangi bonke bese beyamfunga njengoba benifunga futhi bacabanga ukuthi bona baphezulu kokuthize, ngempela bona yibona uqobo abaqambi bamanga"
  58,19,"Wabanqoba usathane manjalo wabenza ukuthi bakhohlwe yisikhumbuzo sikaMvelinqangi, labo bayingxenye kasathane ngokungangabazeki ngempela yiqembu likasathane bona bangabalahlekelwe"
  58,20,Ngempela labo abaphikisa uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe labo bayokuba sekudunyazweni
  58,21,"UMvelinqangi waloba phansi ukuthi ngempela ngizonqoba mina kanye nezithunywa zami, ngempela uMvelinqangi uqatha uphakeme ngamandla"
  58,22,"Ngeke ubathole abantu abakholwa kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina bethanda labo abaphikisa uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe noma ngabe ngoyise noma amadodana abo noma abafowabo noma umndeni wabo, labo waloba ezinhliziyweni zabo ukholo wayesebaseka ngomoya ovela kuyena futhi abafake ezivandeni okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula bayohlala khona ingunaphakade, uMvelinqangi uyothokoza ngabo futhi bayothokoza ngaye, labo bayiqembu likaMvelinqangi ngempela iqembu likaMvelinqangi bona bangabaphumeleleyo"
  59,1,Kudumisa uMvelinqangi konke okusemazulwini nako konke okusemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  59,2,"Yena uyilowo owakhipha labo abangakholwanga phakathi kwabantu bencwadi ezindlini zabo (emizini yabo) ekuhlanganeni kokuqala anicabanganga ukuthi bayophuma futhi babecabanga ukuthi izinqaba zezindlu zabo ziyobavikela kuMvelinqangi, manjalo uMvelinqangi weza kubona evela lapho babengalindele khona futhi wafaka uvalo ezinhliziyweni zabo bebhidliza izindlu zabo ngezandla zabo kanye nezandla zabakholwayo ngakho-ke yalekani Oh Bantu abanamehlo"
  59,3,Futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yokuthi wabanqumela uMvelinqangi ukudingiswa wayezobajezisa emhlabeni futhi okwabo empilweni ezayo yisijeziso somlilo
  59,4,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi bona babephikisa uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani ophikisa uMvelinqangi ngempela uMvelinqangi unzima ekujeziseni
  59,5,Noma ngabe yiziphi izihlahla zesundu enazigawula noma enazishiya zimile ngezimpande zazo kwakungemvume kaMvelinqangi futhi ukuze adumaze abephula umthetho
  59,6,"(Futhi lokho uMvelinqangi akunika isithunywa sakhe njengempango kuvela kubona, ngalokhu anizange nisheshe ngokugibelwayo amahhashi) namakameli, kepha uMvelinqangi unikeza igunya izithunywa zakhe ngaphezulu kwanoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo, futhi uMvelinqangi wenza zonke izinto"
  59,7,Lokho uMvelinqangi akunikeza isithunywa sakhe njengempango kuvela kubantu basemadolobheni ngakho- ke kungokukaMvelinqangi kanye nesithunywa sakhe nezihlobo nezintandane nabampofu kanye nesihambi ukuze kungasetshenziswa phakathi kwabanothile kunina futhi noma ngabe yini enayinikwa yisithunya ngakho-ke yithatheni futhi noma ngabe yini (isithunywa) esanenqabela yona iyekeni (qhelelanani nayo) futhi nesabe uMvelinqangi ngempela uMvelinqangi unzima ekujeziseni
  59,8,(Kunengxenye yezimpango) ekungeyabafuduki abampofu labo abakhishwa ezindlini zabo (emakhaya abo) nasengcebweni yabo befuna umusa ovela kuMvelinqangi nenjabulo futhi belekelela uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe (ngokukholwa) labo-ke bona bangabaneqiniso
  59,9,"Futhi labo ababenendawo yokuhlala kanye nokholo ngaphambilini okwabo bathanda labo abafudukela kubona futhi bangatholi ezifubeni zabo isidingo kulokho ababekunikeziwe futhi bazikhethela bona uqobo yize ngisho noma ngabe kwakunesidingo salokho futhi noma ngabe ngubani osindisiwe ekufiseni kwakhe, labo bona bangabaphumeleleyo"
  59,10,"Futhi labo abafika ngemva kwabo bathi, “Nkosi yethu! Sithethelele kanye nabafowethu labo ababengaphambilini kwethu enkolweni futhi ungabeki ezinhliziyweni zethu inzondo mayelana nalabo abakholwayo, Nkosi yethu ngempela wena umnene unesihawu"
  59,11,"Awubaboni yini abenza ubuzenzisi bathi kubafowabo labo abangakholwanga phakathi kwabantu bencwadi, “uma nikhishwa ngempela sizophuma kanye nani futhi angeke sihloniphe kunina ngisho noma munye futhi uma nilwiswa ngempela siyonilekelela, futhi uMvelinqangi ungufakazi ukuthi ngempela bona bangabaqamba amanga”"
  59,12,Uma bekhishwa (begxoshwa) abaphumi kanye nabo futhi uma belwiswa angeke babalekelele futhi uma bebalekelela ngempela bayofulathelisa imihlane (yabo) bese bengalekelelwa
  59,13,Ngempela nina ningabasabeka kakhulu ezifubeni zabo kunoMvelinqangi lokho kungenxa yokuthi (ngempela) bona bangabantu abangaqondi
  59,14,"Angekebalwenaninonkengaphandlekokubabesemadolobheni akhiwe abayizinqaba noma ngemumva kwezindonga, ukulwa kwabo (nokungezwani) phakathi kwabo kunzima, ucabanga ukuthi bona bahlangene kulapho izinhliziyo zabo zehlukene, lokho kungenxa yokuthi bona bangabantu abangenawo umqondo"
  59,15,Njengalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo kancane bawuzwa umphumela wodaba lwabo futhi okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu
  59,16,"Njengosathane uma ethi kumuntu, “ungakholwa” ngenkathi lapho engakholwa athi, “ngempela angihlangene nawe, ngempela mina ngiyamesaba uMvelinqangi iNkosi yemihlaba”"
  59,17,Ngakho-ke isiphetho sabo bobabili ukuthi bona bobabili bayokuba semlilweni bayokuba kuwona ingunaphakade futhi lokho ngumvuzo wabenzi bakubi
  59,18,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ukuze umphefumulo ubheke lokho okulethe ngaphambili kwangakusasa futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazi ngalokho enikwenzayo"
  59,19,Futhi ningabi njengalabo abakhohlwa nguMvelinqangi manjalo wenza ukuthi bakhohlwe yimiphefumulo yabo labo- ke yibona abephula umthetho (abayizoni)
  59,20,Abalingani (abafani) abahlali bomlilo kanye nabahlali besivande abahlali besivande bona bangabaphumeleleyo
  59,21,Ukuba sasiyehlisele phansi leQur’an phezulu kwentaba ngempela wawuzoyibona (intaba) izithoba futhi ihlukana phakathi ngenxa yokwesaba uMvelinqangi futhi lezi zibonelo sizenzela abantu ukuze bacabange
  59,22,"Yena unguMvelinqangi, akukho okunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe, isazi sokungabonwa nokubonwayo yena ungonomusa onesihawu"
  59,23,"Yena unguMvelinqangi, akukho okunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe iNkosi, umsulwa, uwukuthula, ikholwa (umgcini wokholo) umgcini wokuphepha, uphakeme ngamandla, uqatha, mkhulu (unobukhosi) udumo malube kuMvelinqangi ngaphezulu kwako konke lokho abamenzela ngako abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni"
  59,24,"Yena unguMvelinqangi, umdali, umenzi (oveza obala akudalile noma akwenzile) umbumbi angawakhe amagama amahle kakhulu kudumisa yena konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  60,1,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ningathathi isitha sami kanye nesitha senu njengabangane nikhombisa uthando kubona kulapho bengakholelwa kuloko okwafika kunina okuyiqiniso, bakhipha (bagxosha) isithunywa kanye nani ngokuba nikholelwa kuMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu, ukube nina naniphuma ukuyozabalaza endleleni yami nokufuna injabulo yami benizobakhombisa uthando esithe futhi mina ngazi kangcono ngaloko enikufihlayo kanye nalokho enikuvezayo futhi noma ngabe ngubani okwenzayo (lokho) phakathi kwenu ngempela uphambukile endleleni eqondile"
  60,2,Uma beninqoba bayokuba yizitha zenu futhi balulele kunina izandla zabo nezilimi zabo ngobubi futhi bafisa ukuthi ningakholwa
  60,3,Angeke zibewusizo kunina izihlobo zenu nezingane zenu ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo uyokwahlulela phakathi kwenu futhi uMvelinqangi lokho enikwenzayo uyakubona
  60,4,"Ngaphambilini naninesibonelo esihle ku-Abraham kanye nalaboabakanyenayengenkathibethikubantubabo“ngempela asihlangene nani kanye nalokho enikukhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi, asikholelwa kunina futhi kuvela phakathi kwethu nani ubutha nenzondo kwangunaphakade kuze kube nikholelwa kuMvelinqangi yedwa, ngaphandle kwenkulumo ka-Abrahamu kuyise (ethi) “ngempela ngizokucelela intethelelo futhi anginawo (amandla) okukwenzela okuthize maqondana noMvelinqangi Nkosi yethu sethembele kuwena futhi ikuwena lapho siphendukela khona futhi kukuwena ukubuyela kokugcina”"
  60,5,"Nkosi yethu! Ungasenzi isilingo kulabo abangakholwanga futhi sithethelele, Nkosi yethu ngempela wena ungophakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani"
  60,6,"Ngeqiniso naninesibonelo esihle kubona, kulowo onethemba kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofulathelayo ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi yena akadingi lutho ungodunyiswayo"
  60,7,"Mhlawumbe uMvelinqangi angenza uthando phakathi kwenu naphakathi kwalabo enaniyizitha nabo, futhi uMvelinqangi unamandla okwenza (zonke izinto) futhi uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo unesihawu"
  60,8,"Akanenqabeli uMvelinqangi kulabo abangalwi nani ngenxa yenkolo futhi abanganigxoshi emakhaya enu ukwenza okuhle kubona nokwenza ubulungiswa kubona, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyabathanda abenza ubulungiswa"
  60,9,"Kuphela uMvelinqangi uyanenqabela kulabo ababelwa nani ngenxa yenkolo futhi banigxosha emakhaya enu futhi balekelela ekugxoshweni kwenu-ukuthi nibe ngabangani nabo, futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza ubungani nabo ngakho-ke labo bayilabo abenza okubi (izoni)"
  60,10,"Oh Nina enikholwa! Uma befika kunina abesifazane abakholwayo bengabafuduki ngakho-ke bahloleni, nguMvelinqangi owazi kabanzi ngokholo lwabo manjalo uma senibazile ukuthi bangamakholwa ningabaphindiseli kwabangakholwa, bona abavumelekile kubona futhi bona (abangakholwa) abavumelekile kubona (abesifazane abakhowayo) futhi nibanike lokho abakusebenzisile, futhi alikho icala kunina uma nishada nabo, uma senibanikile okuqondene nabo (isipho sabo somshado) futhi ningabagcini abesifazane abangakholwa futhi nibuze lokho enakusebenzisa (enakukhokha okuyisipho somshado mehr) futhi bafune lokho abakusebenzisa, lokho yisehlulelo sikaMvelinqangi, uyehlulela phakathi kwenu futhi uMvelinqangi uyazi unobuhlakani"
  60,11,"Futhi uma abanye bamakhosikazi enu behamba kunina beya kwabangakholwa ngakho-ke nikezani labo amakhosikazi abo ahamba okufana (okulingana) nalokho abakusebenzisa, futhi yesabani uMvelinqangi lowo nina eningamakholwa kuye"
  60,12,"Oh Mphrofethi! Uma befika kuwena abesifazane abakholwayo befunga kuwena ukuthi angeke bamenzele ngalutho uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni futhi angeke bantshontshe futhi angeke benze ukuphinga futhi angeke bazibulale izingane zabo futhi angeke benze isibhaceko (inkohliso) abayiqamba phakathi kwezandla zabo nezinyawo zabo futhi angeke bakudelele kokuhle, ngakho-ke yamukela isiqiniseko sabo futhi ubacelele intethelelo kuMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyathethelela unesihawu"
  60,13,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ningabi ngabangane babantu intukuthelo kaMvelinqangi ephezulu kwabo, ngempela baphelelwa yithemba ngempilo ezayo njengoba baphelelwa yithemba ababengakholwa abasemathuneni"
  61,1,Kudumisa uMvelinangi konke okusemazulwini kanye nako konke okusemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  61,2,Oh Nina enikholwayo! Kungani nisho lokho eningakwenzi na
  61,3,Kuzondekile kakhulu kuMvelinqangi ukuthi nisho lokho eningakwenzi
  61,4,Ngempela uMvelinqangi uyabathanda labo abalwayo endleleni yakhe beyimigqa okusengathi bona bayisakhiwo esakhiwe saqina
  61,5,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi uMose ethi kubantu bakhe, “Oh Bantu bami! Kungani ningihlupha kulapho senazi ukuthi mina ngiyisithunywa sikaMvelinqangi kunina” ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebephambuka, waziphambukisa uMvelinqangi izinhliziyo zabo futhi uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abephula umthetho (abayizoni)"
  61,6,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi ethi uJesu indodana kaMariya, “Oh bantwana baka-Israyeli ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa sikaMvelinqangi kunina ngiqinisekisa lokho okwakungaphambilini kwami okuyi-Torah futhi ngingumlethi wezindaba ezinhle ngesithunywa esiza ngemumva kwami igama laso ngu-Ahmad, manjalo kwathi lapho esefika kubona nobufakazi obucacile bathi, “lona ngumlingo ocacile”"
  61,7,Futhi ngubani ongenabo ubulungiswa kakhulu kunalowo oqambela uMvelinqangi amanga kulapho yena ememelwa kwi-Islam futhi uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abayizoni
  61,8,Bafuna ukucisha ukukhanya kukaMvelinqangi ngemilomo yabo kepha uMvelinqangi ungumphelelisi wokukhanya kwakhe ngisho noma ngabe bengakuthandi lokho abangakholwa
  61,9,Yena uyilowo owathumela isithunywa sakhe nokuhola nenkolo eyiqiniso ukuze ayenze igqame ngaphezulu kwazo zonke izinkolo yize noma ngabe bengakuthandi lokho abenzela uMvelinqangi abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni
  61,10,Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ngakube nginikhombise yini uhwebo oluzonisindisa esijezisweni esibuhlungu na
  61,11,Kholwani kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi nizabalaze endleleni kaMvelinqangi ngengcebo yenu nangemiphefumulo yenu lokho kungcono kunina ukube benazi
  61,12,Uyonithethelela izono zenu futhi aningenise ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula kanye nezindawo zokuhlala ezinhle ezivandeni zangunaphakade lokho ukuphumelela okukhulu
  61,13,Futhi okunye enikuthandayo usizo oluvela kuMvelinqangi kanye nokunqoba okuseduzane futhi banikeze izindaba ezinhle abakholwayo
  61,14,"Oh nina enikholwayo! Yibani ngabalekeleli baMvelinqangi njengoba asho uJesu indodana kaMariya kubafundi, “ngobani abasizi bami kuMvelinqangi” abafundi bathi, “thina singabasizi baMvelinqangi” manjalo lakholwa iqembu labantwana bakwa-Israyeli futhi (elinye) iqembu langakholwa ngakho-ke sabalekelela ezitheni zabo babangabanqobi labo abakholwa”"
  62,1,"Kudumisa uMvelinqangi konke okusemazulwini kanye nako konke okusemhlabeni iNkosi, engcwele, ephakeme ngamandla enobuhlakani"
  62,2,Yena uyilowo owathumela phakathi kwabangafundile isithunywa phakathi kwabo sibafundela amavesi akhe futhi sibahlanze futhi sibafundise incwadi nobuhlakani yize noma ngabe ngaphambilini babesekudukeni (ephutheni) elicacile
  62,3,Futhi abanye babo abangakangeni kubona – futhi yena (uMvelinqangi) uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  62,4,Lokho ngumusa kaMvelinqangi uwunikeza lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi ungumnikazi womusa omkhulu
  62,5,"Isibonelo salabo ababethweswe (ababenikezwe) iTorah, bese bengayithwali njengembongolo ethwele umthwalo omkhulu, okubi yisibonelo sabantu labo ababephika amavesi nezimpawu zikaMvelinqangi futhi uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abayizoni"
  62,6,"Ithi, “Oh nina maJuda! Uma nizibiza ngokuthi nina ningabangane baMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwabantu ngakho- ke fisani ukufa uma kungukuthi nina ningabaneqiniso"
  62,7,"Futhi angeke bakufise nakancane ngenxa yalokho okwalethwa yizandla zabo ngaphambilini, futhi uMvelinqangi uyisazi ngezoni"
  62,8,"Ithi, “ngempela ukufa loku enikubalekayo –ngempela kuyohlangana nani bese niphindiselwa esazini sokungabonwa nokubonwayo bese sinitshena ngalokho enanikwenza”"
  62,9,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Uma nimenyezelwa umthandazo ngosuku lwangolesihlanu phuthumani niye enkumbulweni kaMvelinqangi niyeke uhwebo, lokho kungcono kunina uma nina nazi"
  62,10,Ngakho-ke uma sewenziwe (sewuqediwe) umthandazo sakazekani (hambani) emhlabeni nifune umusa kaMvelinqangi futhi nikhumbule uMvelinqangi kakhulu ukuze niphumelele
  62,11,"Futhi uma bebona uhwebo noma injabulo baya kukona begijima futhi bakushiya umile ithi, “lokho okukuMvelinqangi kungcono kunomdlalo nohwebo futhi uMvelinqangi ungongcono kakhulu kunabaphayo”"
  63,1,Uma befika kuwena abazenzisi bethi siyafakaza ukuthi ngempela wena uyisithunywa sikaMvelinqangi futhi uMvelinqangi uyazi ukuthi ngempela wena uyisithunywa sakhe futhi uMvelinqangi uyafakaza ukuthi ngempela abazenzisi baqamba amanga
  63,2,Bathatha izifungo zabo njengesembozo bese bevimbela abantu endleleni kaMvelinqangi ngempela bona okubi yilokho ababekwenza
  63,3,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi bona bakholwa base bengakholwa (bayiyeka inkolo) kwabe sekusicilelwa izinhliziyo zabo manjalo bona bangabe besaqonda (lutho)
  63,4,"Futhi uma ubabona iyakuthokozisa imizimba yabo futhi uma bekhuluma uyayilalela inkulumo yabo, okusengathi bona bayizinkuni ezisekelwe, bacabanga ukuthi konke ukhala (umsindo omubi) uqondene (ubhekene) nabo, bona bayizitha ngakho-ke baqaphele sengathi uMvelinqangi angabaqalekisa (ababhubhise) bheka ukuthi bachezuka kanjani eqinisweni"
  63,5,"Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona, “wozani isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi sizonicelela intethelelo” baphendukisa amakhanda abo futhi ubabona bevimbela (abanye) futhi bona bayaziqhenya"
  63,6,"Kuyefana kubona noma ubacelela intethelelo noma awubaceleli intethelo, akasoze abathethelele uMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abephula umthetho (abayizoni)"
  63,7,"Bona bayilabo abathi, “ningachithi (ningasebenzisi lutho) kulabo abakanye nesithunywa sikaMvelinqangi kuze kube bayahlakazeka futhi angawaMvelinqangi amagugu (umnotho) wamazulu nomhlaba kepha abazenzisi abaqondi”"
  63,8,"Bathi, “uma siphindela eMadina ngempela abahlonipheke kakhulu (abanamandla) bazobagxosha kuyona abazithobile futhi kungokukaMvelinqangi ukuhlonipheka nesithunywa sakhe kanye nabakholwayo kepha abazenzisi abazi”"
  63,9,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ayinganichezukisi ingcebo (umnotho) wenu nezingane zenu enkumbulweni kaMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza lokho ngakho-ke labo, bona bangabalahlekelweyo"
  63,10,"Futhi sebenzisani kulokho esanabela kona ngaphambili kokuba ukufa kufike koyedwa wenu bese ethi, “Nkosi yami kungani ungangiphumuzi okwesikhashana ukuze nginikele futhi ngibe ngomunye wabalungileyo"
  63,11,"Futhi akasoze uMvelinqangi awunike ithuba umphefumulo uma sekufike isikhathi sawo, futhi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo"
  64,1,"Kudumisa uMvelinqangi konke okusemazulwini kanye nako konke okusemhlabeni, ubukhosi bungobakhe futhi ngolwakhe udumo futhi yena uyakwazi ukwenza zonke izinto"
  64,2,Yena uyilowo owanidala manjalo phakathi kwenu kunongakholwa futhi phakathi kwenu kunoyikholwa futhi uMvelinqangi lokho enikwenzayo uyakubona
  64,3,"Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso futhi wanibumba, wakwenza kwakuhle ukubunjwa kwenu futhi kukuyena ukubuyela"
  64,4,Uyakwazi loko okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi uyakwazi loko enikufihlayo kanye naloko enikuvezayo futhi uMvelinqangi uyisazi saloko okusezifubeni
  64,5,Ayifikanga yini kunina indaba yalabo abangakholwanga ngaphambilini base bezwa umphumela wodaba lwabo futhi okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu
  64,6,"Loko kungenxa yokuthi zazifika kubona izithunywa zabo namavesi (nezimpawu) ezicacile kepha bathi, “ngakube ngumuntu osiholayo?” Manjalo abakholwayo futhi baphendukele emumva, futhi akaswele uMvelinqangi, futhi uMvelinqangi akadingi lutho (akaswele lotho) ungodunyiswayo"
  64,7,"Labo abangakholwanga bacabanga ukuthi abasoze bavuswe kwabafileyo ithi, “Yebo ngifunga ngeNkosi yami ngempela niyovuswa kwabafileyo bese ngempela nitshelwa ngaloko enanikwenza, futhi loko kuMvelinqangi kulula"
  64,8,"Ngakho-ke kholwani kuMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe kanye nokukhanya esakwehlisela phansi, futhi uMvelinqangi loko enikwenzayo uyakwazi"
  64,9,Ngosuku ayoniqoqa ngalo (eniqoqela) usuku lokuhlangana lolo ngusuku lokulahlekelwa phakathia kwabo nokuzuza futhi noma ngabe ngubani okholwa kuMvelinqangi futhi enze okulungileyo (uMvelinqangi) uyozisusa kuyena izenzo zakhe ezimbi bese emfaka ezivandeni okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula bayohlala lapho phakathi ingunaphakade loko wukuphumelela okukhulu
  64,10,Futhi labo abangakholwanga futhi baphika amavesi (nezimpawu) zethu labo-ke bangabangane bomlilo bayohlala kuwona ingunaphakade futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona
  64,11,"Asikho isehlakalo esehlakalayo ngaphandle kwemvume kaMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani okholwa kuMvelinqangi, (uMvelinqangi) uyayihola inhliziyo yakhe futhi uMvelinqangi uyisazi sazo zonke izinto"
  64,12,Futhi hloniphani uMvelinqangi nihloniphe nesithunywa kepha uma nifulathelile (ningakwenzi lokho) kuphela (umthwalo) ophezulu kwesithunywa sethu (ukudlulisela) umyalezo ocacile
  64,13,UMvelinqangi ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe futhi ikuMvelinqangi lapho bethembela khona abakholwayo
  64,14,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Ngempela phakathi kwamakhosikazi enu nasezinganeni zenu kunezitha zenu, ngakho-ke baqapheleni futhi uma nithethelela ninganaki futhi nixolela ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo unesihawu"
  64,15,"Kuphela ingcebo yenu (umnotho wenu) kanye nezingane zenu ukulingwa, futhi uMvelinqangi kuyena kunomvuzo omkhulu"
  64,16,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi ngendlela eningakwazi ngayo futhi nilalele futhi nihloniphe futhi nisebenzise (ninikele lokho) kungcono emiphefumulweni yenu futhi noma ngabe ngubani osindisiwe esifisweni sakhe (esibi) ngakho-ke labo bona bangabaphumeleleyo
  64,17,Uma niboleka uMvelinqangi ukweboleka okuhle uniphindaphindela kona futhi anithethelele futhi uMvelinqangi ungobongayo obekezelayo
  64,18,Isazi sokungabonwa nokubonwayo siphakeme ngamandla sinobuhlakani
  65,1,"Oh mphrofethi! Uma nenza isehlukaniso somshado nabesifazane ngakho-ke yenzani isehlukaniso somshado nabo ngokwesikhathi sabo (nilinde isikhathi sabo) futhi nibale isikhathi (sabo) futhi nesabe uMvelinqangi iNkosi yenu, ningabakhiphi abesifazane ezindlini zabo futhi (bona uqobo) bangaphumi (bangahambi) ngaphandle kokuba uma benza umkhuba wokonakala ocacile futhi leyo yimikhawulo kaMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani owedlula imikhawulo kaMvelinqangi ngempela wenza okungalungile emphefumulweni wakhe, awazi uMvelinqangi angaletha emumva kwalokho (okunye) udaba"
  65,2,"Ngakho-ke uma sebesigcwalisekisile isikhathi sabo sokulinda, manjalo babambeni ngendlela enhle (esemthethweni) noma nibadedele abesifazane ngendlela enhle, futhi nibabizele ofakazi ababili abanobulungiswa phakathi kwenu futhi nenzele uMvelinqangi ubufakazi, lokho uyala ngako noma ngabe ngubani okholwa kuMvelinqangi nasosukwini lokugcina, futhi noma ngabe ngubani owesaba uMvelinqangi umenzela indlela ephumayo"
  65,3,"Futhi umnika isabelo ngalapho engacabanganga khona futhi noma ngabe ngubani owethembela kuMvelinqangi ngakho- ke yena umenele, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyayifeza inhloso yakhe, ngempela uMvelinqangi wazibekela zonke izinto isilinganiso"
  65,4,"Futhi labo abangalindele ukuya esikhathini phakathi kwabesifazane benu, uma ninokungabaza ngakho-ke isikhathi sabesifazane sokulinda yizinyanga ezintathu kanye nalabo abangayanga esikhathini kanye nalabo abesifazane abakhulelwe isikhathi sabo sokulinda ukuthi kuze kube babeka phansi umthwalo wabo (kuze kube bayabeletha) futhi noma ngabe ngubani owesaba uMvelinqangi umenzela odabeni lwakhe ubulula"
  65,5,Leyo yimpoqo kaMvelinqangi ayehlisela phansi kunina futhi noma ngabe ngubani owesaba uMvelinqangi uyamsusela izenzo zakhe ezimbi bese emenzela ubemkhulu umvuzo wakhe
  65,6,Bahlaliseni abesifazane lapho nihlala khona ngokungangamandla enu futhi ningabalimazi (ningabahluphi) abesifazane okusengathi niyabacindezela (nifuna bahambe singakashayi isikhathi sabo sokulinda) futhi uma bekhulelwe ngakho-ke chithani (umnotho) kubona kuze kube babeka phansi umthwalo wabo (kuze kube bayabeletha) manjalo uma abesifazane benincelisela ngakho-ke banikezeni imivuzo yabo (iholo labo) bese nenza okuhle phakathi kwenu kepha uma nenzelana ubunzima ngakho-ke uzomncelisela omunye wesifazane
  65,7,"(Lowo) onomnotho (onengcebo) makasebenzise engcebweni yakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani onciphiselwe isabelo sakhe manjalo makasebenzise kulokho akunikwa nguMvelinqangi, uMvelinqangi akawethwesi umphefumulo (okungaphezulu kwawo) ngaphandle kwalokho akunika wona, uMvelinqangi uyobeka emumva kobunzima ubulula"
  65,8,Futhi maningi amadolobha ayevukela impoqo yeNkosi yawo nezithunywa zawo ngakho-ke sawabalela (sawehlulela) ukwehlulela okunzima futhi sawajezisa ngesijeziso esesabekayo
  65,9,"Ngakho-ke (amadolobha) ezwa umphumela wodaba lwawo, futhi ngasosonke isikhathi isiphetho sodaba lwawo ukulahlekelwa"
  65,10,UMvelinqangi wabalungiselela isijeziso esinzima ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi Oh nina Bantu bokuqonda! Labo abakholwayo ngempela uMvelinqangi wasehlisela phansi kunina isikhumbuzo (iQur’an)
  65,11,"(Wathumela phansi) isithunywa sinifundela amavesi kaMvelinqangi acacile ukuze sikhiphe labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungile ebumnyameni sibayise ekukhanyeni futhi noma ngabe ngubani okholwa kuMvelinqangi futhi owenza izenzo ezilungileyo uyomfaka ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula uyohlala lapho phakathi kuzona ingunaphakade, uMvelinqangi uyomenzela isabelo esihle kakhulu"
  65,12,"UMvelinqangi nguyena owadala amazulu ayisikhombisa nokomhlaba okufana nawo, impoqo (yakhe) yehlela phakathi kwako (kokubili) ukuze nazi ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyakwazi ukwenza zonke izinto, nokuthi uMvelinqangi usingethe zonke izinto ngolwazi (lwakhe)"
  66,1,"Oh mphrofethi kungani wenqabela loko uMvelinqangi akwenza kwavumeleka kuwena, ufuna injabulo yamakhosikazi akho, futhi uMvelinqangi uyathethelela unomusa"
  66,2,Ngempela wayenza yabayimpoqo kunina uMvelinqangi inhlambuluko(inkululo) ezifungwenizenufuthiuMvelinqangi ungumvikeli wenu futhi uyisazi unobuhlakani
  66,3,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi umphrofethi ekhuluma imfihlo kwenye yamakhosikazi akhe manjalo (unkosikazi wakhe) watshela (omunye) ngayo wayeseyamvezela uMvelinqangi wayenza yazeka ingxenye futhi wayiyeka ingxenye, manjalo ngenkathi emtshena owesifazane ngako wathi owesifazane ngubani okutshene lokhu, wathi owesilisa (ongumprofethi), “ngitshelwe ngowaziyo ongamele ngolwazi"
  66,4,"Uma nobabili niphendukela kuMvelinqangi ngokuzisola ngempela izinhliziyo zenu nobabili zikuthambekele (loko) futhi uma nesekana ngokuphambene naye ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi yena ungumvikeli wakhe, kanye noGabriyeli kanye namakholwa alungileyo kanye nezingelosi emva kwalokho bangabalekeleli (bakhe)"
  66,5,"Mhlawumbe iNkosi yakhe, uma enza isehlukaniso somshado nani izomshintshela ngamakhosikazi angcono kunani angamamuslim (azinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi) akholwayo, ahloniphayo (aqotho) aphendukela kuMvelinqangi ngokuzisola, ayizikhonzi, azilayo (noma ahamba endleleni kaMvelinqangi) aseke ashade (ngaphambilini) nayizintombi ezigcwele ezingakaze zithintwe"
  66,6,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Yivikeleni imiphefumulo yenu kanye nemindeni yenu emlilweni ozithungelo zawo ngabantu kanye namatshe (ogadwe yizingelosi) ezinonya (ezilukhuni) olunzima, akwenzeki ukuthi zingamhloniphi uMvelinqangi kulokho akuphoqa zona futhi zenza lokho ezikuphoqwayo"
  66,7,"Oh Nina eningakholwa! Ningenzi izaba ngalolusuku, kuphela niyonikwa umvuzo walokho enanikwenza"
  66,8,"Oh Nina enikholwayo! Phendukelani kuMvelinqangi ngokuzisola, ukuzisola kweqiniso iNkosi yenu iyozisusa kunina izenzo zenu ezimbi bese inifaka ezivandeni ekugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula, ngosuku angeke uMvelinqangi amjabhise ngalo umphrofethi kanye nalabo abakholwayo kanye naye, ukukhanya kwabo kuyoba ngaphambili kwabo nangakwezokunene zabo bayothi, “Nkosi yethu siphelelisele ukukhanya kwethu futhi usithethelele ngempela wena wenza zonke izinto”"
  66,9,Oh mphrofethi! Zabalaza ukubhekana nabangakholwa kanye nabazenzisi futhi ubenzima kubona futhi indawo yabo yokuhlala yisihogo futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona
  66,10,"UMvelinqangi wabenzela isibonelo labo abangakholwanga, unkosikazikaNowakanyenonkosikazikaLothi, babengaphansi kwezinceku ezimbili, ezincekwini zethu ezilungileyo ngakho- ke womabili (amakhosikazi) ayengathembekanga ngakho- ke womabili abawuzuzelanga lutho umphefumulo wabo ukubhekana noMvelinqangi futhi kwathiwa, “ngenani emlilweni kanye nabangenayo”"
  66,11,"Futhi wenza isibonelo uMvelinqangi salabo abakholwayo– unkosikazi kaFaro ngenkathi ethi, “Nkosi yami ngakhele eduze nawe indlu esivandeni (ezulwini) futhi ungisindise kuFaro nemisebenzi yakhe futhi ungisindise kubantu abayizoni”"
  66,12,NoMaryam (uMariya) indodakazi ka-Imran okuyiyona eyabuqaphela ubumsulwa bayo ngakho-ke saphefumulela kukona umoya wethu futhi (uMariya) wakholelwa emagameni eNkosi yakhe nasezincwadini zayo futhi (uMariya) wayengomunye wabahloniphayo
  67,1,Ugcwele izibusiso lowo esandleni sakhe okunobukhosi (umbuso) futhi yena unamandla ngaphezulu kwazo zonke izinto
  67,2,Lowo owadala ukufa nokuphila ukuze anilinge ukuthi ngubani wenu ongcono kakhulu ngezenzo futhi yena (uMvelinqangi) uphakeme ngamandla uyathethelela
  67,3,"Lowo owadala amazulu ayisikhombisa elinye phezulu kwelinye angeke usibone isici ezidalweni zonomusa, ngakho-ke phinda ubuke, ngakube uyakubona ukuqhekeka"
  67,4,"Ngakho-ke phinda ukubuka kwakho kabili, kuzobuya ukubona kwakho kuzithobile futhi kukhathele"
  67,5,Futhi ngempela salenza labukeka lilihle izulu eliseduzane ngezibani (izinkanyezi) futhi sazenza (izinkanyezi) zaba yimijikijelokosathane(zivimbelaosathaneukuthibangasondeli ezulwini eliseduzane) futhi sabalungiselela (osathane) isijeziso somlilo ovuthayo
  67,6,Futhi okwalabo abangakholwa eNkosini yabo yisijeziso sesihogo futhi kubi lapho kuyiwa khona
  67,7,Uma bephonswa phakathi kusona bayozwa umsindo waso (ukubhonga kwaso) kulapho sona sibila
  67,8,"Sicishe siqhume (ngenxa) yentukuthelo yaso enkulu, ngasosonke isikhathi uma kuphonswa phakathi kusona iqembu bayobabuza abaqaphi baso (bathi) “ akuzange yini kufike kunina umxwayisi (isithunywa sikaMvelinqangi)"
  67,9,"Bayothi, “yebo ngempela wafika kuthina umxwayisi manjalo samphika sabe sesithi uMvelinqangi akazange ehlisele lutho phansi (eyisambulo) nina (anisho lutho) ngaphandle kokuthi nisekudukeni okukhulu"
  67,10,"Futhi bayothi, “ukube sasilalela noma sasinomqondo sasingeke sibe sezihlalini zomlilo ovuthayo"
  67,11,"Manjalo bayozivuma izono zabo, ngakho-ke azibe kude le izihlali zomlilo ovuthayo"
  67,12,Ngempela labo abesaba iNkosi yabo esithe okwabo yintethelelo kanye nomvuzo omkhulu
  67,13,"Futhi yifihleni inkulumo yenu noma niyiveze, ngempela yena uyisazi saloko okusezifubeni"
  67,14,Ngakube (u-Allah) akamazi yini lowo owadala? Kanti yena (uMvelinqangi) umnene ungamele (zonke izinto)
  67,15,"Yena uyilowo owanenzela umhlaba ukuthi uthobe, ngakho-ke hambani ezindleleni zawo futhi nidle esabelweni sakhe futhi kukuyena (uMvelinqangi) ukuvuswa kwabafileyo"
  67,16,Ngakube nizizwa niphephile yini kulowo osezulwini ukuthi angeke enze umhlaba unigwinye kulapho wona uzamazama
  67,17,Noma nizizwa niphephile yini kulowo osezulwini ukuthi angeke athumele kunina isivunguvungu somoya onamatshe bese niyazi ukuthi sinjani isexwayiso
  67,18,"Futhi ngempela baphika labo ababengaphambilini kwabo, manjalo (bheka) ukuthi sasisibi kanjami isijeziso sami"
  67,19,"Abaziboni yini izinyoni ngaphezulu kwabo zivula amaphiko (kwesinye isikhathi) ziyawavala, akekho ozibambayo ngaphandle konomusa, ngempela yena zonke izinto uyazibona"
  67,20,"Ngakube ngubani lona oyibutho lempi yenu, onilekelelayo ngaphandle konomusa? Ngempela abangakholwa (abekho kwenye indawo) ngaphandle kokuba senkohlisweni"
  67,21,Ngakube ngubani lona onabelayo uma esigodla isabelo sakhe? Kepha baqhubeka nokuqhosha nokubalekela (iqiniso)
  67,22,Ngakube lowo ohamba ehuduleka ngobuso bakhe ungoholwe kangcono noma yilowo ohamba ngqo endleleni eqondile
  67,23,"Ithi, “yena uyilowo owaniveza wanenzela ukuzwa (amadlebe) namehlo kanye nezinhliziyo kuncane lokho enikubongayo”"
  67,24,"Ithi, yena uyilowo owanidala emhlabeni futhi ikuyena lapho niyoqoqelwa khona"
  67,25,"Futhi bathi, “siyofika nini lesisithembiso uma kungukuthi nina ningabaneqiniso”"
  67,26,"Ithi, “kuphela ulwazi lukuMvelinqangi nokuthi kuphela mina ngingumxwayisi ocacile”"
  67,27,"Kephaumasebesibona(isijezisoababexwayiswengaso) siseduze ubuso balabo abangakholwanga bube lusizi futhi kuyothiwa, “naku lokhu enanikumema (isijeziso enanixwayiswe ngaso)”"
  67,28,"Ithi, “ngakube nicabangile uma uMvelinqangi engibhubhisa kanye nalabo abakanye nami noma ebanomusa kuthina, ngakho-ke ngubani ozosindisa abangakholwa esijezisweni esibuhlungu"
  67,29,"Ithi, “yena ungonomusa siyakholwa kuyena futhi sethembele kuyena ngakho-ke nizokwazi ukuthi ngubani osephutheni (osekudukeni) okusobala”"
  67,30,"Ithi, “ngakube nicabangile uma amanzi enu ezika (emhlabeni) ngakube ngubani onganilethela amanzi agelezayo na?”"
  68,1,"Nun, ngifunga ngepeni kanye naloko ezikubhalayo (izingelosi)"
  68,2,"Wena, ngomusa weNkosi yakho awuhlanyi"
  68,3,Futhi ngempela okwakho ngumvuzo ongabalwa (ongapheli)
  68,4,Futhi ngempela wena uyisimo esiphakeme (esisezingeni eliphezulu)
  68,5,Ngakho-ke uzobona futhi (nabo) bazobona
  68,6,Ukuthi ngubani owenu ohlushwe ngokuhlanya
  68,7,"Ngempela iNkosi yakho, yona yazi kangcono ngalowo odukile endleleni yayo futhi yona yazi kangcono ngabaholeleke (endleleni eqondile)"
  68,8,Ngakho-ke ungabahloniphi abaphika (iqiniso)
  68,9,Bafisa ukuthi uthambe ukuze bathambe
  68,10,Futhi ungamhloniphi lowo ofunga ngamanga ojabhisiwe
  68,11,Inhlebi ehamba ngokuhleba (ixabanisa abantu)
  68,12,"Umvimbeli wokuhle, isaphulamthetho, isoni"
  68,13,"Unya, ngale kwalokho ukutholwa (komuntu ongesiyena owaleso sibongo)"
  68,14,Ngenxa yokuthi unengcebo nabantwana
  68,15,"Uma\tefundelwa\tamavesi\tethu\tuthi,\t“izinganekwane zabasendulo”"
  68,16,Siyombeka uphawu ekhaleni
  68,17,Ngempela sabalinga njengoba sazilinga izihlali zesivande (zasezulwini) ngenkathi zifunga ukuthi zizokha izithelo zaso ekuseni
  68,18,Futhi abasho ukuthi uma uMvelinqangi ethanda
  68,19,Ngakho-ke kwafika kuyona (ingadi) inhlupheko (isijeziso) esivela eNkosini yakho kulapho bona belele
  68,20,"Ngakho-ke\tekuseni\t(ingadi)\tyaba\tsengathi\tubusuku obumnyama"
  68,21,Base bebizana ekuseni
  68,22,"(Bethi), “iyani ensimini (esivandeni) senu ekuseni uma nifuna ukukha (izithelo)"
  68,23,Ngakho-ke bahamba kulapho bona beswebeza (bekhulumela phansi)
  68,24,Ukuthi angabibikho kunina umuntu ompofu ongena kusona namhlanje
  68,25,Futhi bahamba ekuseni ngomfutho (benamandla) becabanga ukuthi bazokwazi ukwenza
  68,26,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebesibona bathi, “ngempela sidukile”"
  68,27,Kepha thina singabaphuciweyo
  68,28,"Wathi ongcono kunababo, “angizange yini ngisho kunina (ukuthi) kungani ningamdumisanga (uMvelinqangi)"
  68,29,"Bathi,“udumomalubeeNkosiniyethu! Ngempelasasingabenzi bokubi”"
  68,30,Ngakho-ke abanye babo baphendukela kwabanye besolana
  68,31,"Bathi, “Oh usizi kuthina! Ngempela sasephula umthetho (sasiyizoni)”"
  68,32,"Mhlawumbe iNkosi yethu izosishintshela ngokungcono kunako, ngempela iseNkosini yethu lapho sifisa khona"
  68,33,"Sinjalo isijeziso, futhi ngempela isijeziso sempilo ezayo sikhulu kakhulu ukube benazi"
  68,34,"Ngempela\tokwabalungileyo\teNkosini\tyabo\tyizivande zenjabulo"
  68,35,Ngakube senza amamuslimu njengezigebengu na
  68,36,"Kwenzenjani ngani, nehlulela kanjani"
  68,37,Noma ninencwadi enifunda kuyona
  68,38,Ngempela okwenu kuyona yiloko enikukhethayo
  68,39,"Noma okwenu yizifungo ezivela kuthina ezifinyelela osukwini lokuvuka kwabafileyo, ngempela okwenu yilokhu enikwehlulelayo"
  68,40,Babuze ukuthi ngubani owabo ozokumela loko
  68,41,Noma ngakube okwabo ngabahlanganyeli? Ngakho-ke abeze nabahlanganyeli babo uma kungukuthi baneqiniso
  68,42,Ngosuku lapho umbala uyokwembulwa futhi bayobizelwa ekulaleni phansi bese bengakwazi (ukukwenza lokho)
  68,43,"Amehlo abo ayothotshiswa, ukudumazeka kuyobamboza futhi babemenyelwa ekuguqeni (ekuzithobeni) kulapho bona besesimweni esihle"
  68,44,Ngakho-ke ngiyekeni kanye nalabo abaphika lenkulumo siyobaholela (esijezisweni) lapho bengazi khona
  68,45,"Futhi ngibanike ithuba, ngempela isu lami linamandla"
  68,46,Noma ngakube ubacela umvuzo ukuze bona basindwe yisikweletu na
  68,47,Noma ngakube banokungabonwayo ukuze bona bakubhale phansi na
  68,48,Ngakho-ke bekezela isehlulelo seNkosi yakho futhi ungabi njengomngane wenhlanzi ngenkathi ememeza kulapho yena ewusizi
  68,49,Ukube awuzange ufinyelele kuyena umusa ovela eNkosini yakhe wayezophonswa ehlazekile
  68,50,Ngakho-ke yamkhetha iNkosi yakhe yabe seyimbeka waba ngomunye wabalungileyo
  68,51,"Futhi labo abangakholwa bacishe bakwenze ukhubeke ngamehlo abo, uma bezwa isikhumbuzo futhi bathi ngempela wena uyahlanya"
  68,52,"Kepha\tkona\takuyilutho\tngaphandle\tkwesikhumbuzo semihlaba"
  69,1,Iqiniso elingenakuphikiswa
  69,2,Yini iqiniso elingenakuphikiswa na
  69,3,Futhiyiniekwenzawaziukuthiyiniiqinisoelingenakuphikiswa
  69,4,(Abantu) baThamud naba-A’d basiphika isehlakalo
  69,5,Mayelana (nabantu) baThamud babhujiswa ngomsindo owesabekayo
  69,6,"Futhi mayelana (nabantu) ba-A’d babhujiswa ngomoya obandayo, ovunguzayo"
  69,7,Wawenza kubona waba ubusuku obuyisikhombisa nezinsuku eziyisishiyagalombili ezilandelanayo manjalo ubone abantu beholokohleka phansi okusengathi bona bayiziqu zemithi yesundu
  69,8,Ngakube uyayibona yini insalela yabo na
  69,9,Futhi kwafika uFaro kanye nalabo ababengaphambilini kwakhe kanye namadolobha achithiweyo (agumbukuqiwe) ngokona
  69,10,Futhi abazange basihloniphe isithunywa seNkosi yabo ngakho-ke yababamba ngokubamba okukhulu okubuhlungu
  69,11,"Ngempela, ngenkathi amanzi ephophoza ephakama sanithwala emkhunjini"
  69,12,Ukuzesinenzelewona(umkhumbikaNowa) ubeyisikhumbuzo futhi (lokho) kuzwiwe yindlebe ezwayo
  69,13,Manjalo uma sekushawa icilongo ukushawa (ukufuthwa) okukodwa
  69,14,Futhi kuyothwala umhlaba nezintaba bese kubhidlizwa ngokubhidlizwa okukodwa
  69,15,Ngalolosuku siyokwenzeka isigameko
  69,16,Futhi isibhakabhaka siyodabuka phakathi ngakho-ke sona ngalolosuku siyobantengentenge
  69,17,"Futhi izingelosi ziyokuba semaceleni azo, futhi izingelosi eziyisishiyagalombili ngalolosuku ziyothwala isihlalo sobukhosi seNkosi yakho ngaphezulu kwazo"
  69,18,"Ngalolosuku niyolethwa, ayikho imfihlo yenu eyofihlwa"
  69,19,Manjalo lowo onikezwe incwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sokudla bese ethi yifundeni incwadi yami
  69,20,Ngempela mina bengazi ukuthi ngiyohlangana nokubalelwa kwami
  69,21,Ngakho-ke uyokuba sempilweni yenjabulo
  69,22,Esivandeni esiphakeme
  69,23,Izithelo zaso ziyokuba seduzane
  69,24,"Yidlani\tfuthi\tniphuze\tngentokozo\tngenxa\tyalokho enakuthumela ngaphambili ezinsukwini ezedlulayo"
  69,25,"Futhi mayelana nalowo onikwa incwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sobunxele bese ethi, “Oh ngifisa sengathi angizange nginikwe incwadi yami”"
  69,26,Nokuthi angizange ngazi ukuthi kuyini ukubalelwa kwami (ukwahlulelwa kwami)
  69,27,Ngifisa sengathi kona (ukufa) bekuyisiphetho
  69,28,Awungisizi ngalutho umnotho wami
  69,29,Libhubhile (lisukile) kumina igunya lami
  69,30,Mbambeni nimbophe ngeketango”
  69,31,Bese nimshise esihogweni
  69,32,Bese nimbophela eketangweni ubude balo obungangemikhono engamashumi ayisikhombisa
  69,33,Ngempela yena wayengakholelwa kuMvelinqangi omkhulu
  69,34,Futhi akazange agqugquzele ekondleni ompofu
  69,35,Ngakho-ke namuhla akanaye umngane lapho
  69,36,Futhi akukho ukudla ngaphandle kokuphuma ezilondeni (uma kugezwa izilonda)
  69,37,Akekho ozokudla (lokho) ngaphandle kwezoni
  69,38,Ngifunga ngalokho enikubonayo
  69,39,Nalokho eningakuboni
  69,40,Ngempela kona kuyinkulumo yesithunywa esihloniphekile
  69,41,"Futhi kona akusiyona inkulumo yembongi, kuncane lokho enikukholwayo"
  69,42,"Futhi akusiyona inkulumo yesangoma, kuncane lokho enikukhumbulayo"
  69,43,Yisambulo esivela eNkosini yemihlaba
  69,44,Futhi ukube bewuziqambile ezinye izinkulumo mayelana nathi
  69,45,Ngempela besizombamba ngesandla sokunene
  69,46,"Bese, ngempela besizonquma kuyena umthambo"
  69,47,Futhi akekho noyedwa wenu ongakuvimba (lokho) kuyena
  69,48,Futhingempelayona(iQur’an)iyisikhumbuzokwabalungileyo
  69,49,Futhi ngempela siyazi ukuthi phakathi kwenu kunabaphika (ukholo)
  69,50,Futhi ngempela kuyoba wusizi kwabangakholwa
  69,51,Futhi ngempela kona kuyiqiniso langempela
  69,52,Ngakho-ke dumisa igama leNkosi yakho enkulu
  70,1,Wabuza umbuzi mayelana nesijeziso esizokwenzeka
  70,2,Kwabangakholwa – akekho umvimbi waso
  70,3,Sivela kuMvelinqangi umnikazi wezindlela ezenyukayo
  70,4,Zenyukela kuyena izingelosi kanye nomoya ngosuku isilinganiso salo esiyizinkulungwane ezingamashumi ayisihlanu zeminyaka
  70,5,Ngakho-ke bekezela ukubekezela kuhle
  70,6,Ngempela bona bakubona kukude
  70,7,Kepha sikubona (lokho) kuseduzane
  70,8,"Ngosuku\tlapho\tisibhakabhaka\tsiyoba\tnjengethusi elincibilikayo (noma njengensalela yamafutha)"
  70,9,Futhi izintaba ziyoba njengovolo (angeke zehlukaniseke)
  70,10,Futhi akekho umngane oyobuza (omunye) umngane
  70,11,"Bayokwenziwa ukuthi babonane, isigebengu (onecala) uyofisa ukuthi azihlenge esijezisweni salolosuku ngezingane zakhe"
  70,12,Kanye nonkosikazi wakhe nomfowabo
  70,13,Kanye nesihlobo esiseduze okuyisona esamvikela
  70,14,Kanye nabobonke abasemhlabeni bese kuyamsindisa
  70,15,Lutho! Ngempela kona kungumlilo wesihogo
  70,16,(Umlilo wesihogo) ususa isikhumba (kuze kungasali lutho)
  70,17,Umeme (bonke) labo ababefulathelisa imihlane (yabo) futhi bafulathela (endleleni eqondile)
  70,18,Futhi aqoqe (ingcebo) bese eyayigodla
  70,19,Ngempela umuntu wadalwa wangabi nokubekezela
  70,20,Uma ethintwa okubi akabekezeli
  70,21,Futhi uma ethintwa okuhle uyancishana
  70,22,Ngaphandle kwabathandazayo
  70,23,Labo abasemthandazweni wabo njalo
  70,24,Kanye nalabo emnothweni wabo ekunelungelo elaziwayo
  70,25,Lesicelo kanye nonqatshelwe
  70,26,Kanye nalabo abakholelwa osukwini lokwahlulelwa
  70,27,Kanye nalabo abesaba isijeziso seNkosi yabo
  70,28,Ngempela isijeziso seNkosi yabo akusona abazizwa bephephile kusona
  70,29,Kanye nalabo abalondoloza izitho zabo zangasese
  70,30,"Ngaphandle kumakhosikazi abo noma labo abasezandleni zabo zokunene, ngakho-ke ngempela bona abasibona bokusolwa"
  70,31,"Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngobani abafisa okungale kwaloko manjalo labo, bona bephula umthetho"
  70,32,"Nalabo, bona abakugcinayo loko abathenjwe ngako kanye nesivumelwano"
  70,33,"Kanye nalabo, bona abama baqine ebufakazini babo"
  70,34,"Kanye nalabo, bona abagcina umthandazo wabo"
  70,35,Labo bayokuba sezivandeni behloniphekile
  70,36,Ngakho-ke kwenziwa yini ukuthi labo abangakholwanga bajahe ngaphambili kwakho
  70,37,Ngakwesokunene nangakwesobunxele isixuku sabantu
  70,38,Ngakube wonke umuntu phakathi kwabo ufisa ukungena esivandeni senjabulo
  70,39,Lutho! Ngempela sabadala ngalokho abakwaziyo
  70,40,"Manjalo\tngifunga\tngeNkosi\tyezimpumalanga nezintshonalanga, ukuthi ngempela siyakwazi ukwenza"
  70,41,Ukuthi sibashintshe ngabangcono kunabo futhi thina asibona abokushiywa
  70,42,Ngakho-ke bayeke bagxambuze enkulumweni eyize futhi badlale kuze kube bayahlangana ngosuku lwabo lolo abathenjiswa lona
  70,43,"Ngosuku abayophuma ngalo emathuneni ngokushesha, okusengathi bona bajahe esithixweni"
  70,44,"Amehlo abo athotshisiwe ukudumazeka kuyobamboza, lolo wusuku ababethenjiswe lona"
  71,1,Ngempela samthumela uNowa ebantwini bakhe (sathi) xwayisa abantu bakho ngaphambi kokuba sifike kubona isijeziso esibuhlungu
  71,2,"Wathi, “Oh Bantu bami! Ngempela mina kunina ngingumxwayisi ocacile”"
  71,3,Ukuthi nikhonze uMvelinqangi futhi nimesabe futhi ningihloniphe
  71,4,"Uyonithethelela izono zenu bese eninika ithuba kuze kube yisikhathi esinqunyiwe, ngempela isikhathi sikaMvelinqangi uma sifika angeke sihlehliswe ukube benazi"
  71,5,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela ngibamemile abantu bami ubusuku nemini”"
  71,6,Kepha akuzange kubanezelele (ngalutho) ukubamema kwami ngaphandle kokubaleka
  71,7,"Futhi ngempela, ngasosonke isikhathi uma ngibamema ukuze ubathethelele babeka iminwe yabo emadlebeni abo futhi bazimboze ngezingubo zabo futhi babelesela, futhi beqholosha ngokuqholosha okukhulu"
  71,8,Bese ngempela mina ngibabiza ngaphambili kwabo bonke abantu
  71,9,Bese ngempela mina ngamemezela kubona futhi (ngakhuluma) nabo kwabayimfihlo esithe
  71,10,"Ngakho-ke ngathi celani intethelelo yeNkosi yenu, ngempela yona ngasosonke isikhathi iyathethelela"
  71,11,Iyokwehlisela isibhakabhaka (imvula) phezulu kwenu iphophoza
  71,12,Futhi inandisele engcebweni nasezinganeni bese inenzele izivande futhi inenzele imifula
  71,13,Kungani ngani ukuthi ningathembeli ebukhulwini obuvela kuMvelinqangi
  71,14,Kulapho (uMvelinqangi) anidala izigaba ezehlukene
  71,15,Aniboni yini ukuthi wawadala kanjani uMvelinqangi amazulu ayisikhombisa elinye phezulu kwelinye
  71,16,"Futhi wabeka inyanga kuwona yaba ukukhanya, futhi wabeka ilanga labayisibani"
  71,17,Futhi uMvelinqangi wanikhulisa emhlabeni ngokukhula
  71,18,Bese enibuyisela kuwona (umhlaba) futhi anikhiphe
  71,19,Futhi uMvelinqangi wanenzela umhlaba wandlaleka
  71,20,Ukuze nihambe kuwona ezindleleni ezibanzi
  71,21,"UNowawathi,“Nkosiyamingempelabonaabangihloniphanga balandela lowo eyingamnezeleli (ngalutho) ingcebo yakhe nezingane zakhe ngaphandle kokulahlekelwa”"
  71,22,"Futhi benza icebo, icebo elikhulu"
  71,23,"Futhi bathi, “ningabashiyi onkulunkulu benu (izithixo zenu) futhi ningamshiyi uwadd noma usuwa’a noma uyaghuth noma uya’uq no nasr”"
  71,24,Futhi ngempela badukisa abaningi futhi akuzinezezeli (ngalutho) izoni ngaphandle kokuduka
  71,25,Ngenxa yezono zabo baminziswa base bengeniswa emlilweni ngakho-ke bangazitholeli abalekeleli ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi
  71,26,"Futhi uNowa wathi, “ungazishiyi emhlabeni izihlali ezingakholwa”"
  71,27,Ngempela wena uma ubashiya baphambukisa izinceku zakho futhi angeke bazale (lutho) ngaphandle kwesoni esingakholwa
  71,28,Nkosi yami ngithethelele kanye nabazali bami kanye nalowo ongena endlini yami eyikholwa kanye namakholwa esilisa namakholwa esifazane futhi akubanezeleli (ngalutho) abayizoni ngaphandle kokubhubha
  72,1,"Ithi, “kwambulwa kumina ukuthi lilalele iqembu lamajinn ngakho-ke lathi ngempela siyizwile iQur’an emangalisayo"
  72,2,Eholela endleleni elungile ngakho-ke sikholelwe kuyona futhi asisoze senzele iNkosi yethu namuntu umhlanganyeli ekuyikhonzeni
  72,3,"Futhi yona, abuphakanyiswe ubukhulu beNkosi yethu ayizange ithathe unkosikazi nendodana"
  72,4,Futhi izithutha phakathi kwethu zazisho ngoMvelinqangi okubi kakhulu (ukungahloniphi)
  72,5,Futhi sasicabanga ukuthi abantu namajinn abasoze bamqambele uMvelinqangi amanga
  72,6,Futhi ngasosonke isikhathi amadoda angabantu ayefuna isiphephelo emadodeni angamajinn ngakho-ke babanezelela ngomthwalo (wezono)
  72,7,Futhi bona bacabanga njengoba nanicabanga ukuthi akasoze uMvelinqangi avuse (athumele ngisho) noyedwa
  72,8,"Futhi sasifuna ukufinyelela ezulwini, kepha salifica ligcwaliswe ngabaqaphi abaqatha namalangabi omlilo"
  72,9,Futhi sasijwayele ukuhlala lapho phakathi (sibe) sezimweni zokulalela kepha noma ngabe ngubani olalelayo manje uzozitholela umlilo (ilangabi) elivuthayo
  72,10,Futhi asazi noma okubi kuqondiswe kulabo abasemhlabeni noma iNkosi yabo ihlose ngabo ukuholeka
  72,11,"Futhi abanye phakathi kwethu bangabalungileyo futhi abanye phakathi kwethu abayikona lokho, sasiyizindlela ezehlukene"
  72,12,Futhi sasicabanga ukuthi asisoze siphunyuke kuMvelinqangi emhlabeni futhi angeke siphunyuke kuyena ngokubaleka
  72,13,"Futhi ngenkathi sizwa ukuholwa sakholelwa kukona, ngakho- ke noma ngabe ngubani okholwa eNkosini yakhe manjalo akesabi ukunciphiselwa noma umthwalo wokwehlulelwa"
  72,14,Futhi phakathi kwethu kunama muslim futhi phakathi kwethu kunabangenabo ubulungiswa ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani ozinikelayo ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi manjalo labo baziqokele indlela elungile
  72,15,Futhi mayelana nabangenabo ubulungiswa bayoba yizinkuni (yizithungelo) zesihogo
  72,16,Futhi ukube babezigcine besendleleni ngempela sasizobaphuzisa amanzi amaningi
  72,17,Ukuze sibalinge lapho futhi noma ngabe ngubani ophambukayo esikhumbuzweni seNkosi yakhe izomngenisa esijezisweni esinzima
  72,18,Futhi amaMasjid angawaMvelinqangi ngakho-ke ningambizi (omunye) umuntu kanye noMvelinqangi
  72,19,Futhi ngenkathi isukuma inceku kaMvelinqangi imbiza bacishe basondele kuyona beminyana
  72,20,"Ithi, “kuphela ngibiza iNkosi yami futhi angiyenzeli namuntu umhlanganyeli ekuyikhonzeni”"
  72,21,"Ithi, “ngempela mina anginalutho olwenu oluwukulimaza noma ukuhola”"
  72,22,"Ithi, “ngempela mina akekho noyedwa ongivikelayo kuMvelinqangi futhi angisoze ngisithole isiphephelo ngaphandle kwakhe”"
  72,23,"(Akuyilutho) ngaphandle kombiko ovela kuMvelinqangi nemiyalezo yakhe, futhi noma ngabe ngubani ongamhloniphi uMvelinqangi\tnesithunywa\tsakhe\tngakho-ke\tngempela okwakhe ngumlilo wesihogo ahlale kuwona ingunaphakade"
  72,24,Kuze kube yilapho sebebona lokho abathenjiswe kona ngakho-ke bayokwazi ukuthi ngubani obuthakathaka kakhulu ngabalekeleli nabancane ngesibalo
  72,25,"Ithi, “angazi noma kuseduze lokho enethenjiswe kona noma iNkosi yami imbekele isikhathi esiqhelile”"
  72,26,Isazi sokungabonwa futhi asazisi ngisho noma munye imfihlo yaso
  72,27,Ngaphandle kwalowo (isazi) esimkhethile ezithunyweni bese senza ukuthi kuhambe ngaphambili kwakhe kanye nangemumva kwakhe umqapheli
  72,28,Ukuze azi (umqapheli) ukuthi zishumayela imiyalezo yeNkosi yabo futhi isingethe konke lokho okukubona
  73,1,Wena ozimbozile
  73,2,Vuka ubusuku ngaphandle (kwesikhathi) esincane
  73,3,Ingxenye yabo (ubusuku) noma unciphise kubona kancane
  73,4,"Noma wenezelele kukona, futhi uyifunde iQur’an ngokufunda okuhle"
  73,5,Ngempela sizophonsa phezulu kwakho inkulumo esindayo
  73,6,Ngempela ukuvuka ebusuku kona kungcono ekuqondeni (iQur’an) futhi kungcono mayelana nenkulumo (ukuyifunda)
  73,7,Ngempela okwakho emini umsebenzi omkhulu
  73,8,Futhi khumbula igama leNkosi yakho futhi uzinikele kuyona ngokuzinikela okuphelele
  73,9,INkosi yempumalanga nentshonalanga ayikho into enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwayo ngakho-ke yithatheni njengomphathi (wezindaba zenu noma umvikeli)
  73,10,"Futhi bekezela kulokho abakushoyo futhi usuke kubona, ukusuka okuhle"
  73,11,Futhi ngiyeke (nabangakholwa) abaphikayo labo abaphila kahle futhi ubanike isikhathi esincane
  73,12,Ngempela kuthina kunezibopho (amaketango) kanye nomlilo ovuthayo
  73,13,Kanye nokudla okubindayo nesijeziso esibuhlungu
  73,14,Ngosuku lapho umhlaba nezintaba kuyonyakaza futhi izintaba ziyoba yizindunduma zenhlabathi ebhidlikayo
  73,15,"Ngempela sathumela kunina isithunywa, ufakazi kunina njengoba sathumela isithunywa kuFaro"
  73,16,Manjalo uFaro akazange asihloniphe isithunywa ngakho-ke samthatha ngokuthatha okubi
  73,17,"Ngakho-ke ningesaba kanjani uma ningakholwa, usuku oluyokwenza ukuthi izingane zibe nezinwele ezimpunga"
  73,18,"Izulu liyodabuka phakathi, ngasosonke isikhathi isithembiso sakhe (uMvelinqangi) siyafezeka"
  73,19,"Ngempela lokhu yisikhumbuzo, ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani othandayo ukuthatha indlela eya eNkosini yakhe"
  73,20,"Ngempela iNkosi yakho yazi ukuthi wena uyavuka (isikhathi) esingangezingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zobusuku noma ingxenye yako noma okuthathu kwako kanye neqembu lalabo abakanye nawe, futhi uMvelinqangi ukala ubusuku nemini, uyazi ukuthi anisoze nakwazi ukwenza lokho, manjalo (uMvelinqangi) waphendukela kunina ngentethelelo ngakho-ke fundani kwi-Qur’an lokho okulula, uyazi ukuthi kuyobakhona phakathi kwenu abagulayo futhi abanye bahamba emhlabeni bafuna umusa kaMvelinqangi futhi abanye bayalwa endleleni kaMvelinqangi, ngakho-ke fundani kuyona (iQur’an) lokho okulula futhi nenze mthandazo futhi nikhokhe izakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) bese niboleka uMvelinqangi ukuboleka okuhle futhi noma ngabe yini enhle eniyilethela imiphefumulo yenu ngaphambili niyoyithola kuMvelinqangi, yena ungcono futhi mkhulu kakhulu ngomvuzo futhi celani intethelelo kaMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo onesihawu"
  74,1,Oh wena owemboziwe
  74,2,Vuka uxwayise
  74,3,Nenkosi yakho uyidumise
  74,4,Nezingubo zakho uzihlanze
  74,5,Futhi uqhelelane nesinengiso
  74,6,Futhi ungenzi umusa ukuze uzuze okuningi
  74,7,NgeNkosi yakho bekezela
  74,8,Manjalo uma sekushawa icilongo
  74,9,Ngakho-ke lolo wusuku kuyoba wusuku olunzima
  74,10,Kwabangakholwa alulula
  74,11,Ngiyeke kanye nalowo engamdala ngedwa
  74,12,Futhi ngambekela ingcebo enkulu
  74,13,Kanye namadodana (izingane)
  74,14,Futhi ngamenzela (izinto) zabalula
  74,15,Bese efisa ukuthi nginezelele
  74,16,Lutho! Ngempela yena uyisitha sezimpawu zethu
  74,17,Ngiyomphoqa ukuba enyuke
  74,18,Ngempela yena wacabanga futhi wenza ngenhloso
  74,19,"Ngakho-ke\takaqalekiswe\t(akabhujiswe)\twenza\rkanjani ngenhloso"
  74,20,Bese eqalekiswa (ebhujiswa) wenza kanjani ngenhloso
  74,21,Wayese eyabheka
  74,22,Wabe eseyahwaqabala futhi wabheka (kabi)
  74,23,Wayesephindela emumva wazigqaja (waqhosha)
  74,24,"Wayesethi,\t“akuyilutholokhu\tngaphandle\tkomlingo wasemandulo”"
  74,25,Lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kwenkulumo yomuntu
  74,26,Ngiyomfaka esihogweni
  74,27,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi yini isihogo
  74,28,(Isihogo) asishiyi lutho futhi asiyeki lutho (ingashile)
  74,29,Sishisa abantu
  74,30,Phezulu kwaso kuneshumi nesishiyagalolunye
  74,31,"Futhi asizange sibeke abaqaphi bomlilo ngaphandle kwezingelosi futhi asizange sibeke isibalo sazo ngaphandle kwesilingo kulabo abangakholwanga ukuze baqiniseke labo abanikezwa incwadi, futhi banezeleleke enkolweni labo abakholwayo futhi kungabibikho ukungabaza kulabo ababenikezwe incwadi kanye nabakholwayo futhi ukuze labo ezinhliziyweni zabo okunesifo (okunokugula) kanye nabangakholwa bathi, “uqonde ukuthini uMvelinqangi ngalesisibonelo?” Kanjalo uMvelinqangi udukisa lowo amthandayo futhi uhola lowo amthandayo futhi akekho owazi impi (ibutho) leNkosi yakho ngaphandle kwayo futhi kona akuyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo kubantu"
  74,32,Lutho kepha ngifunga ngenyanga
  74,33,Futhi ngifunga ngobusuku ngenkathi buhamba
  74,34,Futhi ngifunga ngokusa ngenkathi kukhanya
  74,35,Ngempela kona kowokunye okukhulu kakhulu
  74,36,Isixwayiso kubantu
  74,37,Kulowo phakathi kwenu othanda ukuya phambili noma ukusala ngemumva
  74,38,Yonke imiphefumulo iyovuma ngalokho okusebenzele
  74,39,Ngaphandle kwabangane bangakwesokunene
  74,40,Bazobasezivandeni bebuzana
  74,41,Ngezigebengu (labo abanecala)
  74,42,Yini enilethe esihogweni na
  74,43,"Bayothi, “sasingeyibona balabo abathandazayo”"
  74,44,Futhi sasingabondli abampofu
  74,45,Futhi sasikhuluma izinkulumo eziyize kanye nabakhulumi beze
  74,46,Futhi sasiluphika usuku lokuhlawula
  74,47,Kwaze kwaba yilapho sifikelwa ukuqiniseka (ukufa)
  74,48,Ngakho-ke akubasizi ngalutho ukuncenga kwabancengeli
  74,49,Ngakho-ke kungani ngabo befulathela isikhumbuzo
  74,50,Okusengathi bona bayizimbongolo zasendle
  74,51,Zibalekela ibhubesi (noma umzingeli)
  74,52,Kepha! Lowo nalowo muntu kubona ufisa ukuthi anikezwe amakhasi avuliwe
  74,53,Lutho! Kepha abayesabi impilo ezayo
  74,54,Lutho! Ngempela yona iQur’an iyisikhumbuzo
  74,55,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani othandayo akayikhumbule
  74,56,"Futhi abakhumbuli ngaphandle kokuba uma ethanda 57. uMvelinqangi, yena ufanelwe ukwesatshwa futhi ufanelwe ukuthethelela"
  75,1,Ngifunga ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo
  75,2,Futhi ngifunga ngomphefumulo ozisolayo (ozithibayo)
  75,3,Ngakube umuntu uyacabanga ukuthi angeke siwahlanganise amathambo akhe
  75,4,Yebo siyakwazi ukuhlanganisa izihloko zeminwe yakho ngendlela enhle
  75,5,Kepha umuntu uthanda ukuthi aqhubeke nokona (enze izono)
  75,6,Uyabuza ukuthi luyofika nini usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo
  75,7,Ngenkathi kuxhopheka ukubona
  75,8,Futhi inyanga iyonyamalala (iyofiphala)
  75,9,Futhi kuyohlanganiswa ilanga nenyanga
  75,10,"Ngalolosuku umuntu uyothi, “ikuphi (indawo) yokubalekela?”"
  75,11,Lutho! Asikho isiphephelo
  75,12,YiseNkosini yakho ngalolosuku lapho kuyoba yindawo yokuhlala (yokuphumula)
  75,13,Uyotshenwa umuntu ngalolosuku ngalokho akuthumela ngaphambili nakushiya ngaphambili
  75,14,Kepha umuntu uyoba ufakazi obhekene naye
  75,15,Ngisho noma ngabe ebeka izizathu zakhe
  75,16,Ungalunyakazisi ngalo (iQuran) ulimi lwakho ukuze usheshise ngayo
  75,17,Ngempela (umthwalo) ophezulu kwethu ukuyihlanganisa kanye nokufundwa kwayo
  75,18,Ngakho-ke ngenkathi siyifunda manjalo landela ukufundwa kwayo
  75,19,Bese ngempela (umthwalo) ophezulu kwethu ukuchazwa kwayo
  75,20,Lutho! Kepha nithanda impilo esheshayo
  75,21,Futhi niyeka impilo ezayo
  75,22,Ubuso ngalolosuku buyokhazimula
  75,23,Bebheke eNkosini yabo
  75,24,Futhi obunye ubuso ngalolosuku buyohwaqabala
  75,25,Becabanga ukuthi bangase behlelwe yisehlo
  75,26,Lutho! Ngenkathi kufinyelela engqwababeni
  75,27,"Futhi kuyothiwa, “ubani ozosindisa"
  75,28,Futhi uyocabanga ukuthi ukwehlikana
  75,29,Futhi umlenze uyohlangana nomunye umlenze
  75,30,Ngalolosuku kuseNkosini ukuqhutshwa
  75,31,Akazange akholwe futhi akazange athandaze
  75,32,Kepha waphika futhi wafulathela (emfundisweni)
  75,33,Wayesehamba eya kubantu bakhe (eziqhenya)
  75,34,Usizi kuwena usizi
  75,35,"Bese (kuba) usizi kuwena, usizi"
  75,36,Ngakube umuntu ucabanga ukuthi uzoyekwa evinjiwe
  75,37,Wayengesilona yini iconsi lesidoda
  75,38,Wayeseba yihlule legazi ngakho-ke (uMvelinqangi) wadala (ubuyena) walinganisa (ubuyena)
  75,39,Wayesenza ngaye okubili isilisa nesifazane
  75,40,Akuyena yini okwazi (unamandla) okuvusa abafile
  76,1,Ngempela ngakube safika yini kumuntu isikhathi lapho ayengeyilutho engacatshangwa
  76,2,Ngempela thina samdala umuntu ngesidoda esihlangene (sowesilisa nowesifazane) samlinga sabe sesimenzela ukuzwa nokubona
  76,3,Ngempela thina samholela endleleni ukuze abe ngobongayo noma ongabongi
  76,4,Ngempela sabalungiselela abangakholwa amaketango namakhamandela nomlilo
  76,5,Ngempela abalungile bayophuzela enkomishini (yewayini) elihlanganiswe namakha
  76,6,"Umthombo okuyophuza khona izinceku zikaMvelinqangi, ziyowenza ukuthi uphophoze ukuphophoza okuhle"
  76,7,Bafeza izifungo futhi besaba usuku ububi balo oluyokwanda (yonke indawo)
  76,8,"Futhi banikeza kanti bayakuthanda loko kudla, ngendlela athanda ngayo osweleyo nentandane kanye nesiqgila"
  76,9,Futhi bethi sinondlela ubuso bukaMvelinqangi – asiwufuni kunina umvuzo noma ukubongwa
  76,10,Ngempela siyesaba eNkosini yethu usuku olulukhuni olunzima
  76,11,"Manjalo uyobasindisa uMvelinqangi ebubini balolosuku, futhi uyokwenza ukuthi bahlangane nobucwazicwazi kanye nenjabulo"
  76,12,Futhi uyobanika umvuzo ngokubekezela kwabo ngesivande kanye nosilika
  76,13,"Bephumulile lapho kusona (isivande) emibhedeni yokucambalala emini, phakathi abaliboni ilanga noma ukubanda okukhulu"
  76,14,Futhi eduzane ngaphezulu kwabo imithunzi yaso (isivande) futhi izithelo zaso ziyolengiselwa eduze kakhulu (ukuze bazithole kalula)
  76,15,Futhi kuyojikeleziswa kubona izitsha zesiliva kanye nezinkomishi zengilazi
  76,16,"Izingilazi (ezenziwe) ngesiliva, ukwenziwa kwazo okulinganisiwe"
  76,17,Futhi bayophuziswa lapho phakathi enkomishini (yewayini) inhlanganisela yayo yijinja
  76,18,Umthombo lapho phakathi (esivandeni) obizwa ngokuthi isalsabil
  76,19,"Futhi bayojikeleza phakathi kwabo abafana bangunaphakade, uma ubabona ucabanga ukuthi bawubuhlalu obuhlakazekile"
  76,20,Futhi uma ubheka (esivandeni ezulwini) uzobona injabulo nombuso omkhulu
  76,21,Phezulu kwabo kuyokuba yizingubo zikasilika ezicolisisekile eziluhlaza nendwangu ehlotshiswe ngokugqamile futhi bayohlotshiswa ngamabhengela esiliva futhi iNkosi yabo iyobaphuzisa isiphuzo esihlanzayo
  76,22,Ngempela lona ngumvuzo wenu futhi ukuzama (ukuzabalaza) kwenu kuyobongeka (kwamukeleke)
  76,23,Ngempela thina sayembula kuwena iQur’an kancane kancane
  76,24,Ngakho-ke bekezelela umthetho weNkosi yakho futhi ungamhloniphi phakathi kwabo oyisoni noma ongakholwa
  76,25,Futhi khumbula igama leNkosi yakho (thandaza) ekuseni nakusihlwa
  76,26,Kanye nasebusuku uyikhothamele (uyiguqele) futhi uyidumise ubusuku obude
  76,27,Ngempela laba bathanda okwamanje (impilo yalomhlaba) bashiya ngemumva kwabo usuku olunzima
  76,28,Thina sabadala saqinisa isimo sabo futhi uma sithanda singabashintsha ngabafana nabo ukubashintsha okuphelele
